00:01:14,036 --> 00:01:18,314
SAVRŠENI SVIJET

3
00:01:51,836 --> 00:01:54,953
- Kad bih ja išla, odjenula bih se...
- Poput kraljevne?

4
00:01:55,156 --> 00:01:56,430
Da.

5
00:01:56,756 --> 00:02:00,066
- Judy Baumer bit ce mažoretkinja.
- Debela je.

6
00:02:00,236 --> 00:02:03,228
Ja bih radije bila Pepeljuga.
Ili Peter Pan.

7
00:02:03,436 --> 00:02:06,030
On je djecak. Z voncica
je djevojcica.

8
00:02:06,196 --> 00:02:11,634
- Phillip bi mogao biti Peter Pan.
- Mogao bi biti samo balvan.

9
00:02:11,956 --> 00:02:15,585
- Zašto ne možemo ici barem jednom?
- Zato jer ne možemo.

10
00:02:15,796 --> 00:02:19,835
Zbog osobnih uvjerenja.

11
00:02:20,796 --> 00:02:24,266
- Ja cu.
- Ti si otvorio prošli put.

12
00:02:24,996 --> 00:02:27,066
Maškare!

13
00:02:27,396 --> 00:02:30,229
Ne sudjelujemo u maškarama.

14
00:02:30,396 --> 00:02:31,590
Molim?

15
00:02:31,916 --> 00:02:33,508
Mi smo
Jehovini svjedoci.

16
00:02:34,476 --> 00:02:37,991
- Zdravo, Phillipe Perry.
- Zdravo, Billy Reeves.

17
00:02:38,516 --> 00:02:40,234
Kako znaš
da sam ja?

18
00:02:40,916 --> 00:02:42,713
Udimo.

19
00:02:43,636 --> 00:02:46,434
Idemo do sljedece kuce.

20
00:02:46,636 --> 00:02:48,592
Oprostite na smetnji.

21
00:03:04,716 --> 00:03:08,425
- Zaboravio si nešto?
- Papire.

22
00:03:09,036 --> 00:03:12,870
- Samo radiš! Kad cemo na pivo?
- Što prije to bolje.

23
00:03:52,236 --> 00:03:54,830
- Hej, tatice?
- Da?

24
00:03:55,916 --> 00:04:00,751
- Siguran si da ovo ide do cijevi?
- Nekad jest.

25
00:04:01,276 --> 00:04:04,791
Ako sada ne ide, išcupat cu ti jezik.

26
00:04:05,716 --> 00:04:07,308
Klipan.

27
00:04:39,516 --> 00:04:42,269
Što ako stari nema pravo?

28
00:05:20,996 --> 00:05:23,271
Sad ceš dobiti!

29
00:05:25,476 --> 00:05:27,194
Bombe!

30
00:05:28,676 --> 00:05:30,189
Pogodak!

31
00:05:56,516 --> 00:05:59,508
Ti i ja smo to zacijelo
necime zaslužili.

32
00:06:01,316 --> 00:06:04,388
Da se razumijemo.
Ne svidaš mi se.

33
00:06:04,556 --> 00:06:06,786
Kad izademo...

34
00:06:06,956 --> 00:06:08,469
...razdvajamo se.

35
00:06:11,836 --> 00:06:14,304
Tko kaže da se ti
svidaš meni?

36
00:06:40,996 --> 00:06:42,429
Drži jezik
za zubima!

37
00:06:44,076 --> 00:06:47,591
Kako bih ti volio prosuti mozak!

38
00:06:56,796 --> 00:06:58,514
'Noc, Larry!

39
00:07:07,836 --> 00:07:09,906
'Noc, Larry.

40
00:07:21,436 --> 00:07:23,586
Probudite se!

41
00:07:34,436 --> 00:07:36,233
Svida mi se onaj.

42
00:07:36,396 --> 00:07:39,866
Izbirljiv si. Ovo nije podrucje
za Lincolne.

43
00:07:40,476 --> 00:07:42,865
Eno Buicka.

44
00:07:43,036 --> 00:07:46,267
Necu Buick nego Ford.

45
00:07:46,476 --> 00:07:50,264
Fordovima curi ulje.
Osim toga, auto je auto.

46
00:07:55,916 --> 00:07:58,066
Uzmi Buicka.

47
00:07:58,716 --> 00:08:02,391
I hocu. Kad predemo granicu.

48
00:08:04,916 --> 00:08:09,034
Dosta mi je cekanja.
Pogledat cu uokolo.

49
00:08:11,036 --> 00:08:13,106
Možda nadem Ford.

50
00:08:41,676 --> 00:08:44,065
Probudi sestre.

51
00:09:06,076 --> 00:09:07,987
Ja ih volim pecena.

52
00:09:33,156 --> 00:09:35,670
Bljutava su.

53
00:09:35,876 --> 00:09:40,552
Dodaj mi kecap. Molim te.

54
00:09:46,236 --> 00:09:49,273
Nemaš muškarca u kuci?

55
00:09:51,876 --> 00:09:53,229
Ne!

56
00:10:04,716 --> 00:10:06,866
Prava tigrica!

57
00:10:07,676 --> 00:10:08,665
Ne!

58
00:10:09,996 --> 00:10:13,671
Gle, imamo u kuci muškarcica.

59
00:10:17,516 --> 00:10:18,710
Ne!

60
00:10:19,876 --> 00:10:21,150
Ne!

61
00:10:30,636 --> 00:10:32,433
Krvarim. Jesi li
sad sretan?

62
00:10:52,556 --> 00:10:54,069
Kako se zoveš,
djecace?

63
00:10:55,876 --> 00:10:57,025
Phillip.

64
00:10:59,316 --> 00:11:03,070
Phillipe, sagni se i podigni revolver.

65
00:11:09,156 --> 00:11:11,272
- Daj mi ga.
- Zaveži!

66
00:11:18,596 --> 00:11:21,747
Uzmi ga i donesi mi ga.

67
00:11:43,916 --> 00:11:45,144
Uperi ga
prema meni.

68
00:11:50,756 --> 00:11:52,030
Uperi ga!

69
00:11:54,356 --> 00:11:56,995
Sada reci: "Ruke u vis!"

70
00:12:01,196 --> 00:12:03,107
Ruke u vis!

71
00:12:06,156 --> 00:12:07,305
Savršeno.

72
00:12:14,956 --> 00:12:17,424
Spusti pušku, starce.

73
00:12:18,716 --> 00:12:23,267
Spusti je. Promašit ceš
i pogoditi djecaka.

74
00:12:24,276 --> 00:12:25,595
Neka zvoni.

75
00:12:26,076 --> 00:12:27,634
Mama?

76
00:12:28,836 --> 00:12:29,951
U redu je, dušo.

77
00:12:30,156 --> 00:12:33,034
- Jesi li gluh?
- Spusti je na tlo.

78
00:12:33,676 --> 00:12:34,950
Spusti je.

79
00:12:35,596 --> 00:12:37,348
Spusti je!

80
00:12:39,596 --> 00:12:41,154
Prekini!

81
00:12:41,516 --> 00:12:43,188
- Povedimo je.
- Ne!

82
00:12:43,476 --> 00:12:48,072
Kako cemo se izvuci bez taoca?
Cijelo je susjedstvo budno.

83
00:12:49,316 --> 00:12:52,433
- Uzet cemo djecaka.
- Ne!

84
00:13:05,636 --> 00:13:08,434
Zar niste culi da se
može duže spavati?

85
00:13:30,036 --> 00:13:32,152
Razumijem, gospodine.

86
00:13:34,356 --> 00:13:37,314
Tisak ceka vec sat vremena.

87
00:13:37,516 --> 00:13:38,585
Shvacam.

88
00:13:46,676 --> 00:13:49,395
Da. Shvacam.
Razumijem.

89
00:13:49,596 --> 00:13:51,109
Razumijem.

90
00:13:52,716 --> 00:13:57,346
Ovdje sam. Slušam vas.

91
00:14:01,916 --> 00:14:03,429
Što je rekao?

92
00:14:03,596 --> 00:14:05,507
- Tko?
- Guverner.

93
00:14:05,676 --> 00:14:09,385
Podsjetio me da je izborna godina.

94
00:14:11,316 --> 00:14:14,467
Nadam se da ne pijete
prije podneva.

95
00:14:15,396 --> 00:14:17,307
Ne pijem.

96
00:14:17,516 --> 00:14:22,067
Zadnja koju smo imali izgledala je
kao da je na dijeti tekucinom.

97
00:14:22,716 --> 00:14:25,071
- Zadnja?
- Tajnica.

98
00:14:25,276 --> 00:14:26,675
Penny Monroe.

99
00:14:26,956 --> 00:14:30,631
DošIo je do zabune.
Iz Huntsvillea sam.

100
00:14:30,796 --> 00:14:33,185
Šalje me guverner.

101
00:14:33,676 --> 00:14:35,792
Što je ovo, Adlere?

102
00:14:35,996 --> 00:14:41,195
Nešto mi zvoni. Jutros su mi
poslali obavijest o njoj.

103
00:14:41,396 --> 00:14:44,706
- Tko?
- Guverner.

104
00:14:45,396 --> 00:14:49,912
Ja sam Sally Gerber.
Zatvorska kriminologinja.

105
00:14:50,116 --> 00:14:54,314
Tom Adler. Teksaški rendžer.

106
00:14:55,636 --> 00:15:00,073
Ovo je relativno novi propis.
Guverner me pridodao...

107
00:15:00,276 --> 00:15:04,508
"Ekipi policije kad god radi
na krivicnim slucajevima."

108
00:15:04,716 --> 00:15:07,833
Ništa se ne kaže o...

109
00:15:08,036 --> 00:15:12,507
Ukljucuje uvjetna puštanja i bjegove.

110
00:15:12,676 --> 00:15:14,553
Evo nas odmah.

111
00:15:14,716 --> 00:15:18,504
Nestrpljivi su.
Ti si odredio vrijeme.

112
00:15:21,156 --> 00:15:24,387
Razumijevanje slucaja
pomoci ce da kod...

113
00:15:24,556 --> 00:15:29,676
...uvjetnog oslobadanja subjekt
izbjegne uobicajene zamke.

114
00:15:29,836 --> 00:15:31,906
Kad je bijeg u pitanju...

115
00:15:32,076 --> 00:15:36,547
...otkrivamo te iste zamke i tako
pomažemo pri hvatanju.

116
00:15:38,036 --> 00:15:42,154
- Da rašcistimo, gdice Gerber.
- Sally.

117
00:15:42,316 --> 00:15:44,113
Reci cu ti, Sally.

118
00:15:44,316 --> 00:15:47,945
Ovo nije krivicni slucaj bijega.
Ovo je lov na ljude.

119
00:15:48,156 --> 00:15:51,466
Razgovori nam nece pomoci.

120
00:15:52,076 --> 00:15:55,671
- Što ce pomoci?
- Pseci njuh...

121
00:15:55,876 --> 00:15:59,789
...i mnogo kave.

122
00:16:17,956 --> 00:16:21,869
Imamo desetak metaka, a on
gada rezervoare s vodom.

123
00:16:22,916 --> 00:16:25,350
Bistro, ha?

124
00:16:34,316 --> 00:16:36,671
Kvragu!

125
00:16:42,876 --> 00:16:46,471
Dosta je bilo. Šef ima posla.

126
00:16:48,836 --> 00:16:51,031
- 'Jutro, Rede.
- 'Jutro.

127
00:16:51,196 --> 00:16:53,949
- Što kažeš?
- Dobro izgleda.

128
00:16:54,116 --> 00:16:56,107
Stvarno smo ponosni
na ovu bebicu.

129
00:16:56,276 --> 00:16:59,712
Guverner ga je narucio kako bi se
dužnosnici vozili u mimohodu.

130
00:16:59,916 --> 00:17:03,955
- Predsjednik Kennedy stiže u Dallas.
- Cuo sam.

131
00:17:05,516 --> 00:17:08,553
Najnovija tehnologija.
Pojacani motor.

132
00:17:08,756 --> 00:17:11,907
Kuhinja. Soba za spavanje.

133
00:17:12,076 --> 00:17:14,067
Ima spremište oružja...

134
00:17:14,276 --> 00:17:18,030
...kuhalo, frižider i direktnu
vezu s guvernerovim uredom.

135
00:17:18,196 --> 00:17:20,187
Krasan primjerak.

136
00:17:20,356 --> 00:17:23,268
Nakon Dallasa je tvoj.

137
00:17:23,476 --> 00:17:27,708
Savršen za mnogo toga.
Stožer na kotacima.

138
00:17:28,276 --> 00:17:29,675
Uzimamo ga.

139
00:17:30,236 --> 00:17:33,706
Prekini snimati! Rede...

140
00:17:33,876 --> 00:17:38,870
- Guverner sutra mora biti u mimohodu.
- Dao je prioritet potjeri.

141
00:17:39,076 --> 00:17:41,988
Rede! Vjeruj mi da...

142
00:17:42,156 --> 00:17:44,875
- Kako se zoveš?
- Dick Suttle. Vozac sam.

143
00:17:45,036 --> 00:17:49,029
- Nisi više.
- On ostaje s vozilom.

144
00:17:49,236 --> 00:17:52,706
- Poznaješ sve naprave u autu?
- Poznajem.

145
00:17:52,876 --> 00:17:55,106
Udi i sjedni.

146
00:17:55,276 --> 00:17:56,868
Rede.

147
00:17:57,396 --> 00:18:01,309
Ovo je Bobby Lee. Strucnjak FBl-a.

148
00:18:01,996 --> 00:18:04,385
Žele da pode s nama.

149
00:18:07,636 --> 00:18:10,628
Što da kažem guverneru?

150
00:18:10,836 --> 00:18:14,749
Reci mu da je gdica Sally Gerber...

151
00:18:15,036 --> 00:18:18,312
...iz njegova ureda
odobrila vozilo.

152
00:18:20,756 --> 00:18:22,587
Kvragu!

153
00:18:29,996 --> 00:18:31,270
Hej!

154
00:18:48,836 --> 00:18:51,555
Ideš li ili ne ideš?

155
00:19:06,196 --> 00:19:08,790
Ni ogrebotine, jesi li cuo?!

156
00:19:08,996 --> 00:19:13,512
Ni ogrebotine! I nazovi me!

157
00:19:24,116 --> 00:19:26,471
Zašto si stao?

158
00:19:27,876 --> 00:19:31,585
- Rekao si da tu blizu imaš rodaka.
- Pa?

159
00:19:32,476 --> 00:19:36,310
Nazovi ga. Možda nas može sakriti
dok se ne slegne prašina.

160
00:20:03,596 --> 00:20:05,791
Zašto je uzeo kljuceve?

161
00:20:07,596 --> 00:20:09,666
Da ga ne ostavim.

162
00:20:12,036 --> 00:20:13,992
Bi li ga ostavio?

163
00:20:16,956 --> 00:20:18,184
O, da!

164
00:20:47,876 --> 00:20:49,912
Zacijelo se odselio.

165
00:20:50,556 --> 00:20:54,834
Ionako ga ne bih cuo.
Krvari mi iz uha.

166
00:20:55,036 --> 00:20:58,312
- Ponovi to i...
- Što?

167
00:20:58,876 --> 00:21:00,070
Što?

168
00:21:01,516 --> 00:21:03,825
Prijetio si mi.

169
00:21:04,476 --> 00:21:06,512
Nije bila prijetnja.

170
00:21:06,956 --> 00:21:08,753
To je cinjenica.

171
00:21:12,076 --> 00:21:14,385
Mali, prihvati volan.

172
00:21:17,516 --> 00:21:20,110
Za 2 sekunde
slomit cu ti nos.

173
00:21:20,276 --> 00:21:21,345
To je prijetnja.

174
00:21:31,836 --> 00:21:34,066
I cinjenica.

175
00:21:35,076 --> 00:21:36,873
Ubit cu te
zbog ovoga.

176
00:21:39,116 --> 00:21:41,072
To je prijetnja.

177
00:21:41,876 --> 00:21:44,515
Shvacaš sad razliku?

178
00:22:12,236 --> 00:22:16,195
Phillipe, poslušaj.
Idem kupiti cigarete.

179
00:22:16,396 --> 00:22:20,548
- Donesi pivo.
- Drži ga.

180
00:22:21,396 --> 00:22:24,752
- Uperi ga njemu medu oci.
- Što?

181
00:22:26,316 --> 00:22:29,228
Ako se i pomakne,
povuci obarac.

182
00:22:29,436 --> 00:22:32,508
Ovo. Stavi prst na njega.

183
00:22:38,476 --> 00:22:40,865
Poludio si.

184
00:22:42,516 --> 00:22:45,508
To je cinjenica.
Pocinješ shvacati.

185
00:23:00,476 --> 00:23:03,036
Gdje su sokovi?

186
00:23:03,196 --> 00:23:07,747
Topli su ondje, rashladeni
u hladioniku.

187
00:23:19,916 --> 00:23:22,794
Jesi li kad pucao, mali?

188
00:23:27,796 --> 00:23:31,675
- Prevali te.
- Tišina, covjece.

189
00:23:32,716 --> 00:23:34,149
Ne...

190
00:23:35,236 --> 00:23:38,308
Nikad nisi pucao...

191
00:23:38,796 --> 00:23:43,551
...jer živiš s tri ženske. Bez tatice.

192
00:23:46,276 --> 00:23:49,188
Vjerojatno ceš postati peder.

193
00:23:55,876 --> 00:24:01,189
Nagnut cu se. Sasvim polako.

194
00:24:02,036 --> 00:24:03,310
U redu?

195
00:24:04,196 --> 00:24:06,915
Tako da možemo razgovarati.

196
00:24:09,516 --> 00:24:11,871
Evo.

197
00:24:12,356 --> 00:24:15,553
Sad možemo razgovarati,
muškarac s muškarcem.

198
00:24:17,356 --> 00:24:19,995
Sad si muškarac.

199
00:24:21,676 --> 00:24:26,033
- To je sve?
- Još onu šteku cigareta gore.

200
00:24:28,676 --> 00:24:32,555
Imaš slatke gacice.

201
00:24:33,156 --> 00:24:37,229
Sigurno ti mama prišiva
inicijale na njih.

202
00:24:40,156 --> 00:24:42,989
Da vidimo što to imaš dolje?

203
00:24:46,156 --> 00:24:48,351
Sicušan je.

204
00:24:50,916 --> 00:24:53,225
Ruka je brža od oka.

205
00:25:00,076 --> 00:25:05,867
Gad! Nema metaka.

206
00:25:11,436 --> 00:25:14,394
Približi se.

207
00:25:16,276 --> 00:25:19,234
- Jesu li to meci za.38?
- Jesu.

208
00:25:19,396 --> 00:25:21,352
Dajte mi kutiju.

209
00:25:23,956 --> 00:25:26,072
Kvragu! Isuse!

210
00:25:29,076 --> 00:25:30,395
Isuse!

211
00:25:49,436 --> 00:25:50,710
Dodi, djecace!

212
00:25:57,796 --> 00:25:59,787
Sve ti je oprošteno.

213
00:26:03,396 --> 00:26:07,105
Najbolje da dodeš.
Znaš da cu te naci.

214
00:27:04,876 --> 00:27:09,996
Mali, najbolje je za tebe
da te ne pronadem.

215
00:27:16,276 --> 00:27:19,109
Što ceš uciniti?
Udariti me revolverom?

216
00:27:25,316 --> 00:27:27,511
Hej, prijatelji smo.

217
00:27:54,476 --> 00:27:56,512
Imate li telefon?

218
00:27:57,556 --> 00:27:58,955
Nemam.

219
00:28:00,356 --> 00:28:03,268
Udite i legnite dok ne odemo.

220
00:28:12,396 --> 00:28:14,307
Ideš li?

221
00:28:18,156 --> 00:28:19,589
Upadaj.

222
00:28:41,996 --> 00:28:47,070
Imam ga. Trgovina blizu
Ben Hura. 80 km odavde.

223
00:28:47,276 --> 00:28:51,588
Prebaci barikade na 288,
80 km sjeverno.

224
00:28:51,756 --> 00:28:55,795
- Tako su daleko stigli?
- Ne znam. A ni oni.

225
00:28:55,956 --> 00:28:59,790
Sretni su što su vani.
Na nedjeljnjoj vožnji.

226
00:29:00,076 --> 00:29:04,592
Nedjeljnja vožnja? Svida mi se.
Nisi još upotrijebio taj izraz.

227
00:29:07,236 --> 00:29:09,511
Nešto te muci?

228
00:29:11,476 --> 00:29:14,309
Možda je prerano, ali...

229
00:29:14,476 --> 00:29:18,594
Imate li pomocni plan
ako se razdvoje?

230
00:29:18,756 --> 00:29:21,429
Misliš da ce to uciniti?

231
00:29:21,596 --> 00:29:24,872
Ako te nešto muci, reci to.

232
00:29:25,676 --> 00:29:31,353
Njihov je problem prilagodavanje.
Sumnjam da ce dugo biti zajedno.

233
00:29:32,516 --> 00:29:35,030
Haynes i Pugh
su suprotnosti.

234
00:29:35,196 --> 00:29:39,428
Haynes je ideal svih kriminalaca.
Oružane pljacke, sukobi.

235
00:29:39,596 --> 00:29:44,545
Pughov je dosje prepun ubojstava.

236
00:29:44,716 --> 00:29:48,345
- Uskoro ce se razdvojiti.
- Što je s taocima?

237
00:29:48,556 --> 00:29:51,024
Bacat ce novcic da vide
tko ce zadržati koga?

238
00:29:51,516 --> 00:29:53,825
Vec se dogadalo.

239
00:29:54,316 --> 00:29:59,549
S tom ce se dilemom brzo suociti.
Mi se moramo odmah.

240
00:29:59,716 --> 00:30:02,514
Nemamo dileme. A ni oni.

241
00:30:02,716 --> 00:30:07,790
Ubit ce jednog taoca, zadržat ce
drugog. Ako to vec nisu ucinili.

242
00:30:11,036 --> 00:30:17,066
Postavite barikade na 288 prema
sjeveru, 80 km odavde.

243
00:30:19,116 --> 00:30:21,505
Tocno. 80 km.

244
00:30:21,796 --> 00:30:23,024
Aha.

245
00:30:24,796 --> 00:30:27,230
Moramo razgovarati,
šefe Garnett.

246
00:30:27,476 --> 00:30:29,546
Rede.

247
00:30:29,756 --> 00:30:31,269
Rede.

248
00:30:31,756 --> 00:30:34,873
Zašto me tako uporno
pokušavaš osramotiti?

249
00:30:35,076 --> 00:30:38,466
Uporan sam u jednom.
Kad me upoznaš...

250
00:30:38,636 --> 00:30:42,265
...vidjet ceš da ti pomaže
smisao za humor.

251
00:30:42,476 --> 00:30:46,947
Imam smisao za humor. Ali necu
da preko mene glumiš heroja...

252
00:30:47,156 --> 00:30:52,389
...budalama koje misle da si
južnjacki Sherlock Holmes.

253
00:30:52,596 --> 00:30:56,430
O, sranje! Kvragu!

254
00:30:56,636 --> 00:31:01,915
Doktori kažu da te to održava mladim.
Ne znam vrijedi li truda.

255
00:31:02,876 --> 00:31:04,309
To imaš reci?

256
00:31:05,316 --> 00:31:08,149
Prvi put na terenu?

257
00:31:08,356 --> 00:31:12,235
Mislio sam.
Što si uopce ocekivala?

258
00:31:12,876 --> 00:31:15,436
Misliš da sam ja
glupa školarka...

259
00:31:15,596 --> 00:31:18,474
...koja je zalutala u mušku
svlacionicu?

260
00:31:18,636 --> 00:31:21,389
Nisam, da znaš.

261
00:31:21,596 --> 00:31:26,386
Ja sam jedna od dvoje
najinteligentnijih ljudi u ovome.

262
00:31:26,636 --> 00:31:29,992
Nisam te to pitao. Pitao sam
što ocekuješ?

263
00:31:30,156 --> 00:31:35,549
Ocekujem da me pustiš da obavim
zadatak koji mi je dao guverner.

264
00:31:36,276 --> 00:31:41,111
Guverner mi je drag. Jednom na
godinu idemo u lov na prepelice.

265
00:31:41,316 --> 00:31:45,514
Obojica znamo da je ovo
moje podrucje. Jasno?

266
00:31:45,676 --> 00:31:49,305
Shvatila sam.
Ali ovo je ipak anarhija.

267
00:31:49,516 --> 00:31:53,350
Govno, da upotrijebim
kaubojski rjecnik.

268
00:31:53,516 --> 00:31:57,668
Reci cu ja tebi što je govno.
Odgovornost.

269
00:31:57,836 --> 00:32:01,351
Besane noci.

270
00:32:01,556 --> 00:32:05,549
Ako ovdje bude krvi, a moglo bi,
guverner gubi nekoliko glasova.

271
00:32:05,756 --> 00:32:08,270
Ja sam onaj koji...

272
00:32:12,636 --> 00:32:18,347
Reci cu ti što cemo. Vidiš li
da sam pogriješio, upozori me.

273
00:32:18,556 --> 00:32:21,229
Možda se ne složim s tobom,
ali saslušat cu te.

274
00:32:21,436 --> 00:32:25,668
Uvrijedim li koga, castit cu ga picem
kad ovo prode.

275
00:32:25,876 --> 00:32:30,427
Sad imam vece brige. Je li pošteno?

276
00:32:32,236 --> 00:32:33,715
Da.

277
00:32:34,756 --> 00:32:38,874
- U redu. Tko je drugi?
- Drugi?

278
00:32:39,756 --> 00:32:42,634
Rekla si, dvoje pametnih.
Tko je drugi?

279
00:32:43,196 --> 00:32:46,472
Haynes.
Testirali smo ga u zatvoru.

280
00:32:54,796 --> 00:32:56,149
Hvala.

281
00:33:00,156 --> 00:33:01,828
Hoceš li me ubiti?

282
00:33:03,076 --> 00:33:04,555
Necu.

283
00:33:05,596 --> 00:33:07,951
Prijatelji smo.

284
00:33:14,716 --> 00:33:19,585
Da sam mogao birati partnera,
uvijek bih prvo izabrao tebe.

285
00:33:23,116 --> 00:33:26,950
- Sigurni ste da su oni?
- Samo je djecak talac.

286
00:33:27,116 --> 00:33:30,074
Našli smo ovo.

287
00:33:37,076 --> 00:33:38,395
Da.

288
00:33:39,276 --> 00:33:42,074
Sad bar znamo tko je glavni.

289
00:33:44,716 --> 00:33:47,867
Jesi li se vozio u vremeplovu?

290
00:33:48,356 --> 00:33:51,905
- Što misliš da je ovo?
- Auto.

291
00:33:53,396 --> 00:33:58,868
Sve vidiš pogrešno.
Ovo je vremeplov 20. stoljeca.

292
00:33:59,076 --> 00:34:02,352
Ja sam kapetan,
a ti navigator.

293
00:34:03,916 --> 00:34:10,105
Naprijed je buducnost.
Otraga je prošIost.

294
00:34:10,316 --> 00:34:14,389
Ako je život prespor i želiš se
preseliti u buducnost...

295
00:34:14,556 --> 00:34:17,275
...daj gas.

296
00:34:17,716 --> 00:34:19,274
Vidiš?

297
00:34:20,916 --> 00:34:25,671
Želiš li usporiti,
staneš na kocnicu...

298
00:34:25,876 --> 00:34:28,674
...i usporiš stroj.

299
00:34:34,036 --> 00:34:37,870
Ovo je sadašnjost.
Uživaj dok traje.

300
00:34:48,676 --> 00:34:52,555
Putujemo Teksasom kroz vrijeme.

301
00:34:56,636 --> 00:35:01,232
Moramo naci Ford.
Moj je tata uvijek vozio Ford.

302
00:35:06,716 --> 00:35:08,866
Ovo je interkom.

303
00:35:09,076 --> 00:35:13,467
On pomaže u prenosu podataka.

304
00:35:13,676 --> 00:35:17,828
- Kako radi?
- Ukljucite ga.

305
00:35:18,036 --> 00:35:21,028
Ali ako je preglasno...

306
00:35:21,196 --> 00:35:22,788
Bradley, kvragu!

307
00:35:23,276 --> 00:35:25,915
Uništit cete zvucnike.

308
00:35:29,876 --> 00:35:33,391
To ce ga sjebati. Oprostite.

309
00:35:33,556 --> 00:35:36,753
Prostacki humor. Jedinstven. Ne bi li
i tu trebale biti barikade?

310
00:35:36,956 --> 00:35:39,151
U savršenom svijetu...

311
00:35:39,316 --> 00:35:43,025
...bismo cešljali šumu
dok ga ne nademo.

312
00:35:43,236 --> 00:35:46,911
U savršenu se svijetu
takvo što ne bi ni dogodilo.

313
00:35:49,876 --> 00:35:53,346
Mjesni policajci. Da ih slijedimo?

314
00:35:54,476 --> 00:35:59,596
Ne. Kružit cemo. S vremenom
ce negdje iskrsnuti.

315
00:36:21,796 --> 00:36:24,230
Idemo u kupnju auta.

316
00:36:24,436 --> 00:36:27,234
Jesi li se vec igrao kauboja
i Indijanaca?

317
00:36:29,196 --> 00:36:30,948
Vidiš li onaj Ford?

318
00:36:32,796 --> 00:36:36,869
Prišuljaj mu se poput Indijanca
i zaviri...

319
00:36:37,076 --> 00:36:39,510
...je li kljuc u autu.

320
00:36:42,636 --> 00:36:45,196
Ne moraš ako ne želiš.

321
00:36:45,356 --> 00:36:49,190
Ali bio bih ti zahvalan.
Navigator si.

322
00:36:59,116 --> 00:37:01,425
Phillipe!

323
00:37:01,716 --> 00:37:04,310
Pogledaj ima li i radio!

324
00:37:29,836 --> 00:37:33,112
Ima kljuceve i radio.
Provjerio sam.

325
00:37:34,156 --> 00:37:35,589
Odlicno.

326
00:37:35,796 --> 00:37:38,629
Možemo li stati kod
benzinske crpke?

327
00:37:40,276 --> 00:37:43,746
- Zašto?
- Piški mi se.

328
00:37:46,076 --> 00:37:50,354
Priroda je oko tebe.
Popiški se uz drvo.

329
00:39:13,916 --> 00:39:16,908
- To je moj auto!
- Gad!

330
00:39:30,676 --> 00:39:32,553
Udi u auto!

331
00:39:33,836 --> 00:39:35,986
Phillipe, u auto!

332
00:39:36,476 --> 00:39:37,955
Upadaj!

333
00:40:01,516 --> 00:40:05,668
- Koliko si Cola popio?
- Cetiri.

334
00:40:14,476 --> 00:40:17,627
<i>Smijemo li pucati,</i>
<i>ako bude prilike?</i>

335
00:40:17,836 --> 00:40:21,670
Mještani pitaju smiju li pucati
ako bude prilike.

336
00:40:27,436 --> 00:40:28,869
Ne.

337
00:40:31,996 --> 00:40:36,512
Ne želim da se neki narednik poigra
svojom puškom na jelene.

338
00:40:36,716 --> 00:40:41,392
- Trebali bi. Ima djecaka.
- Mislite da ce se predati?

339
00:40:43,116 --> 00:40:47,951
- Možda hoce, možda nece.
- No to je sigurna prognoza.

340
00:40:48,156 --> 00:40:50,954
Reci cu vam jednu sigurnu.
U boljem je položaju nego prije.

341
00:40:51,156 --> 00:40:55,354
Metak medu Pughovim ocima
govori drukcije.

342
00:40:55,556 --> 00:40:58,514
Zašto ga onda ne ubijemo?

343
00:40:59,276 --> 00:41:01,028
Javio se pametni.

344
00:41:01,196 --> 00:41:04,472
Javili su barikadama broj auta.

345
00:41:04,676 --> 00:41:09,511
- Još idemo na farmu?
- Da. Imam predosjecaj.

346
00:41:11,876 --> 00:41:14,515
Još nisam upoznao
smedookog Phillipa.

347
00:41:14,716 --> 00:41:18,675
- Po kome si dobio ime?
- Tati.

348
00:41:19,476 --> 00:41:23,185
- Slažeš li se sa starim?
- Slažem.

349
00:41:23,396 --> 00:41:27,275
Igrate se loptom i provodite
vrijeme zajedno?

350
00:41:27,516 --> 00:41:29,188
Ne.

351
00:41:30,636 --> 00:41:32,388
Zašto?

352
00:41:33,436 --> 00:41:35,427
Zapravo ga nema.

353
00:41:36,876 --> 00:41:39,231
Ima ga ili nema?

354
00:41:43,076 --> 00:41:45,795
Kad si ga zadnji put vidio?

355
00:41:52,956 --> 00:41:56,232
Ti i ja imamo mnogo toga
zajednickog.

356
00:41:57,076 --> 00:41:59,431
Obojica smo zgodni
vragolani...

357
00:41:59,956 --> 00:42:01,912
...obojica volimo Cole.

358
00:42:02,156 --> 00:42:05,512
Obojica imamo oca ništariju.

359
00:42:09,916 --> 00:42:14,706
Mama kaže da ce se vratiti.
Vjerojatno kad mi bude 10 g.

360
00:42:16,276 --> 00:42:19,109
Laže ti.

361
00:42:19,996 --> 00:42:22,954
Nece se vratiti.

362
00:42:28,156 --> 00:42:30,590
Decki poput nas...

363
00:42:30,796 --> 00:42:33,264
...moraju biti samostalni.

364
00:42:33,796 --> 00:42:36,230
Tražiti glupu sudbinu.

365
00:42:36,436 --> 00:42:39,109
Ili slicno.

366
00:42:45,156 --> 00:42:48,273
Ti si zadužen za održavanje
automobila?

367
00:42:48,476 --> 00:42:51,707
Jesam. Vozac sam.

368
00:42:51,916 --> 00:42:55,750
Stalno se vraca u drugu.

369
00:42:55,916 --> 00:42:59,625
Možda netko ima tešku nogu.

370
00:42:59,836 --> 00:43:02,987
Provjerio bih to da sam
na tvome mjestu.

371
00:43:07,316 --> 00:43:08,874
Pa...

372
00:43:09,236 --> 00:43:12,353
Hvala Bogu, nema nikoga.

373
00:43:14,436 --> 00:43:16,472
- Našao si kljuceve auta?
- Nisam.

374
00:43:17,436 --> 00:43:20,906
Donesi mi polugu.

375
00:43:27,916 --> 00:43:29,474
Izvoli.

376
00:43:29,676 --> 00:43:33,589
- Pricekaj u prikolici.
- Molim te.

377
00:43:43,756 --> 00:43:46,224
Evo našeg birokrata.

378
00:43:58,276 --> 00:44:02,394
Dobro je znati da je mali
u dobrim rukama. Izvoli.

379
00:44:02,596 --> 00:44:05,429
Crni humor, Sally.

380
00:44:05,636 --> 00:44:08,708
Bez njega, svi bismo
izbacivali rucak.

381
00:44:10,116 --> 00:44:13,267
- Želite li vode?
- Ne.

382
00:44:39,436 --> 00:44:42,234
Hoceš li te gace
zamijeniti hlacama?

383
00:44:42,436 --> 00:44:44,631
Idemo onda.

384
00:44:47,916 --> 00:44:53,036
Prvo moramo smisliti pseudonim.
Znaš, lažno ime.

385
00:44:53,236 --> 00:44:56,831
Tako cemo se oslovljavati
pred drugima.

386
00:44:57,036 --> 00:44:59,596
Smisli ime.

387
00:44:59,756 --> 00:45:02,634
- Ime koje želiš.
- Koje želim?

388
00:45:02,796 --> 00:45:04,275
Koje želiš.

389
00:45:09,836 --> 00:45:13,226
Dobro došli u Friendly's.

390
00:45:13,436 --> 00:45:15,745
Cini se da djecak
treba hlace.

391
00:45:15,956 --> 00:45:20,711
Zajedno s cipelama i donjim rubljem.
Reci ce vam broj.

392
00:45:20,916 --> 00:45:22,952
Buzz, podi s gospodom.

393
00:45:23,516 --> 00:45:27,555
- Buzz.
- Buzz, podi s gospodom.

394
00:45:27,756 --> 00:45:30,509
Slatko ime, Buzz.
Poput bumbarcica.

395
00:46:01,156 --> 00:46:04,944
Gle, ljubazni duh. Reci "bu"!

396
00:46:05,516 --> 00:46:07,188
Bu.

397
00:46:07,396 --> 00:46:12,390
Nisi nikoga uplašio. Ali vježbat ceš
godinu dana. Ako ti tata da.

398
00:46:12,556 --> 00:46:16,390
Što si bio ove godine?

399
00:46:16,796 --> 00:46:18,434
Bandit.

400
00:46:34,596 --> 00:46:36,393
Sranje!

401
00:46:36,796 --> 00:46:38,275
- Pete?
<i>- Da?</i>

402
00:46:38,476 --> 00:46:40,751
Ja sam. Mislim
da sam ga našao.

403
00:46:44,636 --> 00:46:47,992
- Što mislite?
- Dobre su.

404
00:46:50,636 --> 00:46:53,912
Hoce li to biti sve za danas?

405
00:46:56,596 --> 00:47:00,384
Nikad još nisam vidio da se
netko toliko smiješi.

406
00:47:05,676 --> 00:47:08,349
Svaki mjesec imamo
natjecanje.

407
00:47:08,556 --> 00:47:12,390
Najljubaznija prodavacica dobiva
bonus od 20 dolara.

408
00:47:19,436 --> 00:47:21,666
Spreman sam. A ti?

409
00:47:22,676 --> 00:47:27,431
Spreman. Zadržimo ga dok
ne stigne pojacanje.

410
00:47:27,596 --> 00:47:30,190
<i>Lov na Butcha Haynesa...</i>

411
00:47:30,396 --> 00:47:33,991
<i>... bjegunca iz Huntsvillea,</i>
<i>nastavlja se.</i>

412
00:47:34,196 --> 00:47:39,554
<i>Haynes, 1,85 m visok, 84 kg,</i>
<i>smedokos, naoružan je i opasan.</i>

413
00:47:39,756 --> 00:47:42,475
<i>- Viden je...</i>
- Evo i odjece.

414
00:47:42,636 --> 00:47:47,585
Buzz se oduševio kostimom za
maškare. Snižen je 50 posto.

415
00:47:48,476 --> 00:47:53,106
<i>... cetiri milje južno od Desdemona.</i>
<i>Vjeruje se...</i>

416
00:47:53,316 --> 00:47:57,628
<i>... da Haynes drži kao taoca</i>
<i>osmogodišnjeg djecaka.</i>

417
00:47:57,836 --> 00:48:01,033
<i>Policija je danas našla i leš</i>
<i>zatvorskog službenika...</i>

418
00:48:01,196 --> 00:48:04,632
Kupit cemo ga drugi put.
Cekaj me u autu, sinko.

419
00:48:04,836 --> 00:48:08,875
<i>... Haynes s taocem,</i>
<i>i ostali bjegunci, Terry Pugh.</i>

420
00:48:09,396 --> 00:48:12,547
<i>Billingov leš naden je u
<i>prtljažniku njegova auta...</i>

421
00:48:12,716 --> 00:48:15,469
<i>... nedaleko od farme...</i>

422
00:48:15,916 --> 00:48:20,546
<i>... na kojoj je jutros</i>
<i>ukraden drugi auto.</i>

423
00:48:20,756 --> 00:48:23,395
<i>Ukradeni je auto žuti Ford.</i>

424
00:48:23,596 --> 00:48:27,794
<i>Vidite li ga, javite policiji.</i>

425
00:48:27,996 --> 00:48:31,113
<i>Kao što smo javili,</i>
<i>tijelo Terryja Pugha...</i>

426
00:48:31,276 --> 00:48:34,507
Vi ste najljubaznija
prodavacica koju znam.

427
00:48:38,116 --> 00:48:41,313
Hvala što ste kupovali kod nas.

428
00:49:35,756 --> 00:49:37,235
Kvragu!

429
00:49:42,836 --> 00:49:44,872
Što, do vraga...?!

430
00:49:54,556 --> 00:49:55,909
Vraca se!

431
00:50:00,636 --> 00:50:03,628
- Makni se!
- Sranje!

432
00:50:06,036 --> 00:50:09,108
Znala sam da nešto ne valja.

433
00:50:30,636 --> 00:50:33,230
Pogledaj, ostavio je sina.

434
00:50:37,356 --> 00:50:39,995
Ima Casperov kostim!
Ukrao ga je!

435
00:50:47,116 --> 00:50:50,791
Buzz, ti malo govno,
krada je zlocin.

436
00:50:52,756 --> 00:50:55,065
Ti odluci, Buzz!

437
00:51:01,676 --> 00:51:05,191
Neceš se izvuci!

438
00:51:08,556 --> 00:51:10,831
I niste baš tako ljubazni.

439
00:51:38,156 --> 00:51:41,705
Skini te prljave gace i odjeni hlace.

440
00:51:45,676 --> 00:51:49,715
- Što je to?
- Kostim duha.

441
00:51:49,916 --> 00:51:51,429
Iz trgovine?

442
00:51:52,796 --> 00:51:54,024
Maznuo si ga?

443
00:51:58,076 --> 00:52:00,670
Obuci ga.

444
00:52:01,476 --> 00:52:03,273
Nisi ljut?

445
00:52:05,236 --> 00:52:09,434
Razjasnimo nešto. Ružno je krasti.

446
00:52:09,636 --> 00:52:13,868
Ali ako nešto želiš,
a nemaš novca da to kupiš...

447
00:52:14,036 --> 00:52:16,709
...nije loše posuditi to.

448
00:52:16,876 --> 00:52:20,186
To je iznimka od pravila.

449
00:52:23,116 --> 00:52:24,595
Što ne valja?

450
00:52:25,476 --> 00:52:27,114
Sve je u redu.

451
00:52:28,316 --> 00:52:31,626
Neceš se skinuti preda mnom?

452
00:52:34,356 --> 00:52:37,951
Sramiš se da vidim tvoga pišu?

453
00:52:39,916 --> 00:52:41,508
Pa...

454
00:52:41,676 --> 00:52:43,189
Sicušan je.

455
00:52:45,116 --> 00:52:47,107
- Što?
- Sicušan je.

456
00:52:49,196 --> 00:52:51,266
Tko ti je to rekao?

457
00:52:53,996 --> 00:52:55,714
Da vidim.

458
00:52:58,636 --> 00:53:01,434
Otvoreno cu ti reci.

459
00:53:04,836 --> 00:53:08,624
Ma daj! Prava velicina
za djecaka tvoje dobi.

460
00:53:13,236 --> 00:53:14,988
Evo ih.

461
00:53:37,636 --> 00:53:40,833
Haynes je kupio ljepljivu vrpcu,
užad i odjecu za klinca.

462
00:53:41,036 --> 00:53:44,312
Kažu da je mali mogao pobjeci,
ali nije.

463
00:53:44,516 --> 00:53:47,792
- Vjerojatno je uplašen.
- Još nešto.

464
00:53:47,996 --> 00:53:52,626
- Mali je ukrao kostim za maškare.
- Kakav par!

465
00:53:52,836 --> 00:53:57,114
- Krenuli su u koridor.
- Što?

466
00:53:57,316 --> 00:54:00,388
- Ondje je više cesta nego ljudi.
- Kako to?

467
00:54:00,556 --> 00:54:03,992
Siromašni okrug. Ne završe stare
ceste, a vec pocnu graditi nove.

468
00:54:04,196 --> 00:54:07,188
Ako netko poznaje te
ceste, tada je to Red.

469
00:54:08,076 --> 00:54:09,509
Dobro...

470
00:54:13,676 --> 00:54:19,194
Recimo da sam ja Robert Haynes. Svi
me zovu Butch. Roden sam u Amarillu...

471
00:54:19,396 --> 00:54:22,706
...odrastao u francuskom dijelu
New Orleansa.

472
00:54:22,916 --> 00:54:25,271
Što to ona radi?

473
00:54:26,156 --> 00:54:28,431
Ubio sam covjeka
s osam godina.

474
00:54:30,396 --> 00:54:32,227
Kako?

475
00:54:32,516 --> 00:54:37,032
Revolverom.38. Uvijek bi se našao
koji u plesnoj dvorani.

476
00:54:37,236 --> 00:54:41,514
Tako su je zvali. Zapravo je bila
javna kuca. Ondje smo živjeli.

477
00:54:41,676 --> 00:54:46,147
- Što je ucinila policija?
- Žrtva je bila na popisu traženih.

478
00:54:46,356 --> 00:54:50,474
Sve je bilo zataškano.

479
00:54:50,676 --> 00:54:53,509
Nisu ga poslali
u popravni dom?

480
00:54:53,836 --> 00:54:57,670
U školu. Bio sam u zaostatku 3 g.,
ali sve sam nadoknadio.

481
00:54:57,956 --> 00:55:01,995
- Sve je krenulo na bolje.
- Jest.

482
00:55:02,196 --> 00:55:05,984
- Ali u 12. g. umire mi mama.
- Što se dogodilo?

483
00:55:06,196 --> 00:55:10,826
Objesila se u zahodu javne kuce.

484
00:55:11,036 --> 00:55:14,312
Obdukcija otkriva
zadnji stadij sifilisa.

485
00:55:14,556 --> 00:55:17,992
- Gdje ti je otac?
- Nitko ne zna.

486
00:55:18,156 --> 00:55:22,832
Ostavio nas je kad sam imao 6.
Sitni prijestupnik.

487
00:55:23,036 --> 00:55:25,994
Vratio se kad je mama umrla.

488
00:55:26,196 --> 00:55:30,235
Izašao je na uvjetnu slobodu
pa se selimo u Amarillo.

489
00:55:30,436 --> 00:55:34,793
- Godinu dana poslije sam u nevolji.
- Ubio si nekoga?

490
00:55:36,956 --> 00:55:41,029
Nisam mogao odoljeti Fordu coupeu
i povezao sam se njime.

491
00:55:41,436 --> 00:55:45,031
- Pa što?
- I ja sam tako mislio.

492
00:55:45,196 --> 00:55:50,395
Ali ne i sudac. 4 g. Gatesvillea,
najgoreg doma za maloljetnike.

493
00:55:50,596 --> 00:55:55,545
Ondje je gad postao kriminalac.
To smo vec vidjeli.

494
00:55:58,836 --> 00:56:02,067
Butch, reci nam kamo ideš...

495
00:56:02,236 --> 00:56:04,466
...i prištedi nam
trud lova.

496
00:56:04,676 --> 00:56:07,588
Pogrešno ste sve shvatili.
Nije važno...

497
00:56:07,796 --> 00:56:11,505
...kamo idem
kao zašto idem onamo.

498
00:56:11,716 --> 00:56:14,514
Sranje! Ja bježim,
oni me progone.

499
00:56:14,676 --> 00:56:18,464
Svejedno je kamo idem.

500
00:56:18,676 --> 00:56:20,553
Ovo je salonska igra.

501
00:56:20,716 --> 00:56:24,789
Ali Butch Haynes
nema pojma kamo ide.

502
00:56:28,916 --> 00:56:33,148
Drži kažiprst na crti
koja oznacava ceste.

503
00:56:33,356 --> 00:56:37,713
Imaš tri pregiba na prstu.

504
00:56:37,916 --> 00:56:43,036
Izmedu svake je centimetar. Koliko je
centimetara do Childressa?

505
00:56:44,716 --> 00:56:45,990
Jedan...

506
00:56:46,156 --> 00:56:47,714
...dva...

507
00:56:48,836 --> 00:56:49,985
Šest.

508
00:56:51,916 --> 00:56:54,828
Vraški si dobar navigator.

509
00:56:55,036 --> 00:56:57,550
Mnogo pametniji od Terryja.

510
00:56:58,116 --> 00:57:02,029
Ali kome bi se mogao hvaliti o tome?

511
00:57:04,076 --> 00:57:05,794
Pogledaj!

512
00:57:08,156 --> 00:57:12,069
- Što je to?
- Poput srebrnog kita.

513
00:57:12,276 --> 00:57:16,235
Ima i ljude. Kao Jona iz Biblije.

514
00:57:19,956 --> 00:57:23,631
Ucini ovo, možda i oni zatrube nama.

515
00:57:27,556 --> 00:57:30,992
- Što kažeš?
- Hajde, zatrubi!

516
00:57:36,436 --> 00:57:38,631
Djecak je ukrao
kostim za maškare?

517
00:57:42,076 --> 00:57:45,193
- Kakav?
- Caspera, ljubaznog duha.

518
00:57:46,516 --> 00:57:49,076
- Oni su. Mimoišli smo se.
- Što?!

519
00:57:49,236 --> 00:57:51,147
- To su bili oni!
- Okreni!

520
00:57:51,356 --> 00:57:52,755
Oni su! Okreni!

521
00:58:14,236 --> 00:58:18,627
Ne bi smio voziti brže od 100 km
uz toliki teret otraga.

522
00:58:21,476 --> 00:58:22,909
Brzo nam se
približavaju.

523
00:58:23,716 --> 00:58:25,786
Lezi na stražnjem
sjedalu.

524
00:58:25,996 --> 00:58:29,033
- Zašto?
- Ne znam.

525
00:58:29,196 --> 00:58:30,675
Zato što sam
tako rekao.

526
00:58:32,236 --> 00:58:33,715
Preopterecuješ
motor!

527
00:58:33,876 --> 00:58:35,025
Drži se.

528
00:58:37,396 --> 00:58:39,227
Napravi
širok zaokret.

529
00:58:57,436 --> 00:59:00,792
- Što to radiš?
- Slijedim bjegunca, budalo!

530
00:59:02,556 --> 00:59:03,989
Što sad radiš?

531
00:59:08,436 --> 00:59:09,425
Sranje!

532
00:59:16,036 --> 00:59:17,025
Red?

533
00:59:22,436 --> 00:59:24,233
Red ce biti bijesan.

534
00:59:41,476 --> 00:59:43,273
Želiš li nas ubiti?!

535
00:59:43,436 --> 00:59:44,869
Sranje!

536
00:59:49,396 --> 00:59:51,830
O, Bože!

537
01:00:10,836 --> 01:00:14,795
Žele znati kako je djecak izgledao.

538
01:00:14,996 --> 01:00:18,193
- Smijao se i mahao nam.
- To im nemoj reci.

539
01:00:18,396 --> 01:00:19,715
Ne.

540
01:00:21,716 --> 01:00:25,709
- Rekli su da se djecak doimao dobro.
- Sjajno.

541
01:00:25,916 --> 01:00:28,555
Bit ce dobro.

542
01:00:28,716 --> 01:00:31,389
Zacas cemo to riješiti...

543
01:00:31,596 --> 01:00:35,908
...i vi cete biti sa svojim sinom.
Obecavam.

544
01:00:36,716 --> 01:00:39,628
Osobno sam odobrio...

545
01:00:39,836 --> 01:00:44,512
...upotrebu prikolice u ovoj potjeri.

546
01:00:44,676 --> 01:00:49,989
To je nevjerojatna futuristicka
oprema snaga reda i mira.

547
01:00:57,796 --> 01:01:01,835
Poceli su graditi cestu prije 20
godina. Još je nisu završili.

548
01:01:07,036 --> 01:01:10,028
Moramo sada odluciti.

549
01:01:15,276 --> 01:01:16,595
Ti odluci.

550
01:01:16,796 --> 01:01:20,550
Možemo se vratiti na autocestu
ili nastaviti pješice.

551
01:01:20,716 --> 01:01:22,672
Kamo idemo?

552
01:01:29,716 --> 01:01:31,707
Ovo je Aljaska.

553
01:01:32,156 --> 01:01:34,192
Posljednja
granica divljine.

554
01:01:34,676 --> 01:01:37,429
- Lijepa je.
- Prekrasna.

555
01:01:38,196 --> 01:01:41,745
- Bio si ondje?
- Nisam.

556
01:01:42,556 --> 01:01:45,116
Imam samo jednu razglednicu.

557
01:01:46,316 --> 01:01:49,035
Ali vratimo se našoj dilemi.

558
01:01:49,236 --> 01:01:52,467
- Hoda li ti se?
- Dokle?

559
01:01:52,756 --> 01:01:54,712
Ne može biti više...

560
01:01:55,436 --> 01:01:56,869
...od 2500 km.

561
01:02:02,156 --> 01:02:05,546
Imaš pravo. Provjeri zalihe.

562
01:02:14,636 --> 01:02:20,074
- Onda?
- Sok, žvakaca guma i pola biskvita.

563
01:02:21,076 --> 01:02:23,829
U najboljem je slucaju
to za jednoga.

564
01:02:24,956 --> 01:02:26,309
Dodi.

565
01:02:42,716 --> 01:02:43,944
Rede!

566
01:02:44,116 --> 01:02:49,031
Guverner traži da prikolica bude
sutra na paradi.

567
01:02:51,596 --> 01:02:53,746
Reci mu da dode po nju.

568
01:02:54,076 --> 01:02:55,509
Razumijem.

569
01:03:02,636 --> 01:03:06,549
- Kamo idemo?
- U maškare.

570
01:03:11,756 --> 01:03:15,385
- Što ne valja?
- Ne smijemo ici u maškare.

571
01:03:15,836 --> 01:03:16,951
Ha?

572
01:03:17,356 --> 01:03:19,187
Moja mama to
ne dopušta.

573
01:03:20,236 --> 01:03:23,945
- Zašto?
- To je protiv naše vjere.

574
01:03:24,316 --> 01:03:28,309
Protiv vaše...
Kakva je to glupost?

575
01:03:29,676 --> 01:03:31,268
Jehovini svjedoci.

576
01:03:38,596 --> 01:03:40,791
Phillipe, pitam tebe.

577
01:03:40,996 --> 01:03:43,749
Ne pitam tvoju majku.
Ne pitam Jehovu.

578
01:03:44,076 --> 01:03:46,795
Želiš li poci u maškare?

579
01:04:10,956 --> 01:04:14,028
Trebaš samo pokucati na vrata.

580
01:04:14,236 --> 01:04:18,229
Kad ti otvore, reci: "Maškare!"

581
01:04:32,196 --> 01:04:34,346
Cekaj dok ne dodu.

582
01:04:39,756 --> 01:04:41,155
Sada, Phillipe.

583
01:04:41,356 --> 01:04:43,108
Maškare!

584
01:04:43,436 --> 01:04:46,951
Najsladi mali duh kojega sam vidjela.

585
01:04:47,236 --> 01:04:49,989
- Ponovi.
- Maškare, gospodo!

586
01:04:50,156 --> 01:04:54,388
Ali bile su jucer.

587
01:04:54,596 --> 01:04:59,670
Propustio si kokice s karamelom
koje sam pripremila.

588
01:05:04,236 --> 01:05:06,227
Pricekaj.

589
01:05:07,596 --> 01:05:09,075
Savršeno.

590
01:05:35,196 --> 01:05:37,664
- Kako kažeš?
- Hvala.

591
01:05:48,916 --> 01:05:52,955
Nikada ne podcjenjuj ljubaznost
obicnog covjeka.

592
01:05:53,916 --> 01:05:56,146
Siguran si da
nema mesa?

593
01:05:56,316 --> 01:06:00,946
Konzerviranog? Kobasica?

594
01:06:01,276 --> 01:06:02,629
Nema.

595
01:06:08,236 --> 01:06:12,946
- Možeš napraviti sendvice sa senfom?
- Mogu.

596
01:06:13,116 --> 01:06:14,993
Hajde.

597
01:06:27,876 --> 01:06:30,344
Time možeš mazati.

598
01:06:34,996 --> 01:06:38,466
Ovaj je moj.

599
01:07:14,716 --> 01:07:16,388
Odmah se vracam.

600
01:07:25,356 --> 01:07:28,314
Ne škrtari sa senfom.

601
01:07:52,276 --> 01:07:53,265
Butch!

602
01:07:54,356 --> 01:07:55,630
Butch!

603
01:07:56,716 --> 01:07:59,549
- Phillipe!
- U pomoc!

604
01:08:01,996 --> 01:08:04,794
- Zgrabi djecu! Brzo! Bježi!
- Phillipe!

605
01:08:04,956 --> 01:08:06,514
Zaboravi auto!

606
01:08:09,476 --> 01:08:11,592
Jesi li poludjela? Prošao je
samo 1500 km.

607
01:08:12,276 --> 01:08:14,506
- Stisni kocnicu!
- Butch!

608
01:08:34,916 --> 01:08:38,033
- Loše kocnice.
- Ovo je bilo gusto.

609
01:08:40,716 --> 01:08:42,388
Bob Fiedler.

610
01:08:42,796 --> 01:08:43,990
Edgar Poe.

611
01:08:45,916 --> 01:08:50,432
Na smrt sam se uplašio.
Imam ga tek dva mjeseca.

612
01:08:51,876 --> 01:08:54,470
Krasan je.

613
01:08:54,636 --> 01:08:58,390
Ima problem s kocnicama.
Možete li nas povesti?

614
01:09:01,836 --> 01:09:05,067
Živim sa sinom 8 km odavde.

615
01:09:05,276 --> 01:09:07,915
- Doci cu po auto kad...
- Butch!

616
01:09:14,156 --> 01:09:15,714
Kocnica, Phillipe!

617
01:09:15,876 --> 01:09:17,468
Stisni je!

618
01:09:23,836 --> 01:09:27,192
Sjajno, Phillipe!
Nikad nisam posumnjao.

619
01:09:37,796 --> 01:09:41,152
Edgare, je li vam dobro? Mogu
preseliti djecu sasvim otraga.

620
01:09:41,396 --> 01:09:45,548
Nema potrebe, Bobe. Nema potrebe.

621
01:09:48,076 --> 01:09:49,225
Hvala, gospodine.

622
01:09:56,396 --> 01:09:58,830
Hvala.

623
01:09:58,996 --> 01:10:01,226
Dozvolu, molim vas.

624
01:10:01,436 --> 01:10:04,234
Hvala.

625
01:10:07,596 --> 01:10:11,748
- Dozvolu, molim vas.
- Što se dogodilo?

626
01:10:16,076 --> 01:10:19,591
Odbjegli robijaš. Ovo je samo
predostrožnost. Sretan put.

627
01:10:19,756 --> 01:10:21,348
Hvala.

628
01:10:38,156 --> 01:10:42,593
Mogu nam dati dva patrolna auta.

629
01:10:42,796 --> 01:10:47,745
Neka ostanu gdje jesu.
Mi ovdje imamo najbolja mjesta.

630
01:10:47,916 --> 01:10:51,875
Barikade na jugu neka se pomaknu
na sjever.

631
01:10:52,076 --> 01:10:57,309
Pretražit cemo sve ceste i farme
od San Angela do Sweetwatera.

632
01:10:57,836 --> 01:11:00,031
Kamo sam stavio Geritol?

633
01:11:18,556 --> 01:11:22,595
Patsy, pazi što radiš.

634
01:11:22,796 --> 01:11:24,593
Gledaj što si ucinila!

635
01:11:24,876 --> 01:11:28,107
Što ti je? Gledaj me!

636
01:11:28,276 --> 01:11:32,827
Dvaput sam ti rekla da
ne skaceš. Nisam li?

637
01:11:33,156 --> 01:11:36,592
Prosula si po cijelom
novom tatinom autu.

638
01:11:37,196 --> 01:11:40,632
Sjedite i mirujte.

639
01:11:44,556 --> 01:11:48,265
U redu je, medena.
Tatica te još voli.

640
01:11:50,236 --> 01:11:53,785
Zbogom mirisu novog auta.

641
01:11:55,076 --> 01:11:57,829
Ovdje možete stati.

642
01:12:04,276 --> 01:12:07,586
Zamolit cu vas još jednu uslugu.

643
01:12:23,196 --> 01:12:25,835
Samo ga posudujem.

644
01:12:26,476 --> 01:12:28,512
Dobit cete ga natrag.

645
01:12:32,116 --> 01:12:37,315
Nov je. Bio bih zahvalan da 800 km
ne vozite brže od 70 km/h.

646
01:12:37,556 --> 01:12:40,070
Znate da necu, Bobe.

647
01:12:46,916 --> 01:12:49,669
- Smiješni su.
- Možda.

648
01:12:49,876 --> 01:12:51,867
Ali Bob je
dobro postupio.

649
01:12:52,076 --> 01:12:54,306
Što bi bilo
da se potukao?

650
01:12:54,956 --> 01:12:58,949
Možda bih ga morao ubiti. Što bi
tada bilo s njegovom obitelji?

651
01:12:59,396 --> 01:13:01,751
Ne, Bob je krasan
obiteljski covjek.

652
01:13:01,916 --> 01:13:05,113
To je najbolje u covjeku.

653
01:13:09,436 --> 01:13:11,904
Izdržite,
gotovo smo stigli.

654
01:13:21,876 --> 01:13:24,709
Prošli su Aspermont.
Prisilio je vozaca.

655
01:13:25,156 --> 01:13:29,911
Kvragu! Nazovi Amarillo i reci im
da vjerojatno idu onamo.

656
01:13:31,236 --> 01:13:36,356
Nadam se da ce preci granicu.
Neka ga preuzmu federalci.

657
01:13:37,156 --> 01:13:41,149
Imam posla kod kuce.
Gladan sam. Ima li tu hrane?

658
01:13:41,556 --> 01:13:44,707
Ne znam. Pogledat cu.

659
01:13:45,276 --> 01:13:50,066
- Ima govedih odrezaka.
- Necemo ih dirati.

660
01:13:50,276 --> 01:13:53,552
- Smrznuti pomfrit.
- Nece mu se to svidjeti.

661
01:13:53,716 --> 01:13:55,274
Je li?

662
01:13:57,036 --> 01:13:59,869
Volim smrznuti pomfrit.

663
01:14:00,596 --> 01:14:04,191
Nikako da nadem pravu glazbu!

664
01:14:07,756 --> 01:14:12,466
Ozbiljno si mislio da ne smiješ
u maškare...

665
01:14:12,676 --> 01:14:14,906
...zbog vjere?

666
01:14:15,116 --> 01:14:16,435
Jesam.

667
01:14:17,676 --> 01:14:21,555
- Što još ne smiješ?
- Ne slavimo Božic.

668
01:14:21,716 --> 01:14:25,948
- Sereš?
- Nemamo rodendana ni proslava.

669
01:14:26,956 --> 01:14:30,187
Nikad nisi bio u zabavnom parku?

670
01:14:30,356 --> 01:14:31,675
Ne.

671
01:14:31,996 --> 01:14:35,830
- Ni jeo šecernu vunu?
- Vidio sam je jednom.

672
01:14:36,156 --> 01:14:37,145
Crvena je.

673
01:14:37,396 --> 01:14:39,785
Nije. Ružicasta.

674
01:14:39,956 --> 01:14:41,833
Nikad je nisam jeo.

675
01:14:41,996 --> 01:14:45,113
- Tobogani?
- Vidio sam ih na slikama.

676
01:14:48,396 --> 01:14:53,754
Šecerna vuna i vožnja toboganom
tvoje su americko pravo.

677
01:14:54,156 --> 01:14:55,225
Doista?

678
01:14:56,076 --> 01:14:58,032
Da, doista.

679
01:15:05,516 --> 01:15:09,668
Brže, Butch! Brže!

680
01:15:15,116 --> 01:15:17,152
Brže!

681
01:15:21,956 --> 01:15:24,789
Brže, Butch! Brže!

682
01:15:37,796 --> 01:15:40,230
Navalite!

683
01:15:52,236 --> 01:15:55,273
Misliš da si pametna.

684
01:15:55,436 --> 01:15:56,664
Molim?

685
01:15:57,836 --> 01:16:01,431
Pametna nisi, ali si zgodna.

686
01:16:02,276 --> 01:16:03,265
Ma daj!

687
01:16:03,476 --> 01:16:09,392
Vjerujem da posao i zabavu
treba uvijek kombinirati.

688
01:16:11,636 --> 01:16:15,265
Uzmi mene. Volim svoj posao.

689
01:16:15,876 --> 01:16:17,992
Volio ga je i Hitler.

690
01:16:18,236 --> 01:16:21,148
Dugu jezicinu imaš!

691
01:16:21,316 --> 01:16:23,625
Kakav odrezak voliš, Sally?

692
01:16:24,076 --> 01:16:25,509
Krvav.

693
01:16:25,676 --> 01:16:30,466
Obrisat cu govedu stražnjicu,
dotjerati ga i odreži si jedan.

694
01:16:30,676 --> 01:16:33,793
Kad bolje promislim,
srednje pecen.

695
01:16:36,396 --> 01:16:38,387
Ne tice me se
za koga radiš.

696
01:16:38,556 --> 01:16:42,515
Ovdje si zbog jednog razloga.
Razumiješ?

697
01:16:46,516 --> 01:16:48,711
Još što, šefe?

698
01:16:49,676 --> 01:16:50,950
Da.

699
01:16:51,516 --> 01:16:54,826
U mom si uredu. Gubi se.

700
01:17:00,491 --> 01:17:01,640
KOD DOTTIE

701
01:17:08,971 --> 01:17:10,882
Izvoli.

702
01:17:13,091 --> 01:17:17,084
Hvala, oce, na obilju i dobroti.

703
01:17:18,171 --> 01:17:19,399
Amen.

704
01:17:19,571 --> 01:17:21,402
Navali, Buzz.

705
01:17:21,571 --> 01:17:24,722
Jede poput ptice grabljivice.

706
01:17:25,491 --> 01:17:28,483
Da je mrtvo,
sagnuo bi se i pojeo.

707
01:17:37,771 --> 01:17:39,489
Ti si Dottie?

708
01:17:39,651 --> 01:17:42,245
Eileen. Dottie je umrla.

709
01:17:42,451 --> 01:17:45,090
Njezin sin vodi restoran...

710
01:17:45,251 --> 01:17:47,560
...ali nikad ga nema.

711
01:17:48,371 --> 01:17:49,770
Nikad?

712
01:17:49,971 --> 01:17:55,364
Odlazi u cetiri. Poslije rucka
dok nema mnogo prometa.

713
01:18:10,851 --> 01:18:14,002
Ako me trebaš, ondje sam.

714
01:18:29,811 --> 01:18:31,847
Jedi.

715
01:19:16,571 --> 01:19:20,450
- Buzz, pojedi i moje.
- Ne, hvala.

716
01:19:21,931 --> 01:19:24,126
Vrlo je pristojan.

717
01:19:25,251 --> 01:19:28,607
Trudim se, ali otkad mu je
mama umrla...

718
01:19:28,771 --> 01:19:30,489
Moja mama
nije umrla.

719
01:19:34,131 --> 01:19:38,044
Idi na parkiralište
i bacaj kamencice.

720
01:19:53,371 --> 01:19:57,159
Onda, je li mrtva ili nije?

721
01:19:58,691 --> 01:20:01,888
Njegova je prava majka živa.

722
01:20:02,211 --> 01:20:05,567
Dala ga je na posvojenje
meni i ženi.

723
01:20:06,251 --> 01:20:09,049
Mojoj pokojnoj ženi.

724
01:20:09,251 --> 01:20:12,880
Ona je bila Phill...

725
01:20:13,091 --> 01:20:17,243
Buzzova pomajka. Ona mu je majka.

726
01:20:17,451 --> 01:20:19,009
Bila mu je majka.

727
01:20:19,211 --> 01:20:20,530
Pomajka.

728
01:20:21,651 --> 01:20:23,687
Ali umrla je.

729
01:20:24,571 --> 01:20:27,039
Tako mi je žao.

730
01:21:04,571 --> 01:21:06,004
Znatiželjni momcic.

731
01:21:11,971 --> 01:21:13,768
Ulazi u auto.

732
01:21:31,491 --> 01:21:33,527
Jesi li ljut na mene?

733
01:21:33,771 --> 01:21:35,124
Nisam.

734
01:21:37,571 --> 01:21:39,926
Ljubio si je.

735
01:21:40,691 --> 01:21:42,488
Jedva.

736
01:21:45,251 --> 01:21:46,684
Zašto?

737
01:21:48,131 --> 01:21:50,406
Svida mi se.

738
01:21:50,611 --> 01:21:54,206
Nisi nikad vidio mamu
da ljubi muškarca?

739
01:21:58,851 --> 01:22:00,887
Ljubio si joj
stražnjicu?

740
01:22:03,691 --> 01:22:06,728
To je teško objasniti.

741
01:22:07,491 --> 01:22:10,051
Znam kako je izgledalo.

742
01:22:13,331 --> 01:22:17,210
- Zapravo ne znam.
- Voliš li je?

743
01:22:17,851 --> 01:22:20,843
- Koga?
- Ženu s hamburgerom.

744
01:22:23,011 --> 01:22:24,683
Da, Phillipe.

745
01:22:24,851 --> 01:22:26,489
Da, volim je.

746
01:22:29,891 --> 01:22:32,359
Ljubio joj stražnjicu, ha?

747
01:22:59,171 --> 01:23:01,127
Bude li sve išIo glatko...

748
01:23:01,331 --> 01:23:04,607
...za cetiri-pet dana smo na Aljaski.

749
01:23:06,771 --> 01:23:09,080
Stici cemo prije zime.

750
01:23:17,651 --> 01:23:19,084
Što ne valja?

751
01:23:19,971 --> 01:23:22,405
Želim poci kuci.

752
01:23:23,331 --> 01:23:27,961
- Zašto danas nisi ostao u ducanu?
- Zato.

753
01:23:28,131 --> 01:23:31,760
- Zašto zato?
- Zato što sam ukrao.

754
01:23:32,451 --> 01:23:35,648
Zatvorili bi me.
Otišao bih u pakao.

755
01:23:38,371 --> 01:23:40,680
To je isto, Phillipe.

756
01:23:40,891 --> 01:23:42,370
Isto.

757
01:23:46,651 --> 01:23:48,960
Brzo cu te vratiti kuci.

758
01:23:49,571 --> 01:23:51,084
Dajem ti
casnu rijec.

759
01:23:57,171 --> 01:23:59,287
- Butch?
- Da?

760
01:24:01,891 --> 01:24:03,563
Znam voziti.

761
01:24:06,091 --> 01:24:11,290
To si dokazao.
Mnogo je toga što znaš.

762
01:24:11,451 --> 01:24:16,241
Mnogo toga. Otvori prednji pretinac.

763
01:24:17,891 --> 01:24:20,963
Možda Bob tu ima notes.

764
01:24:22,011 --> 01:24:23,763
Dobri stari Bob.

765
01:24:24,451 --> 01:24:27,090
- Znaš li pisati?
- Tiskanim slovima.

766
01:24:27,291 --> 01:24:28,804
Dovoljno je.

767
01:24:29,011 --> 01:24:34,483
Sastavi popis stvari koje želiš
ciniti, ali ne smiješ.

768
01:24:34,651 --> 01:24:36,050
Kakve?

769
01:24:38,251 --> 01:24:39,889
Poput...

770
01:24:40,731 --> 01:24:42,005
...šecerne vune.

771
01:24:43,091 --> 01:24:44,729
Šecerna vuna.

772
01:24:46,051 --> 01:24:48,440
Kvragu, ne znam.
To je tvoj popis.

773
01:24:54,611 --> 01:24:56,966
- Butch?
- Da?

774
01:24:57,171 --> 01:24:59,765
Kako se piše raketa?

775
01:25:03,251 --> 01:25:06,607
Pustit cu ih da odspavaju.

776
01:25:06,811 --> 01:25:09,644
Još nekoliko sati.

777
01:25:09,851 --> 01:25:14,845
Ujutro cemo dobiti patrolna kola
i odvesti se u koridor.

778
01:25:17,931 --> 01:25:20,923
Budi li to uspomene?

779
01:25:26,611 --> 01:25:28,920
Imaju dosje i o meni?

780
01:25:29,131 --> 01:25:34,205
Šezdesete su. Svatko ima dosje.

781
01:25:34,611 --> 01:25:38,763
Ne znaci da je istina ako je zapisano.

782
01:25:38,971 --> 01:25:41,166
Slažem se.

783
01:25:41,331 --> 01:25:45,165
Bio si šerif u Amarillu i Austinu...

784
01:25:45,331 --> 01:25:48,004
...prije nego što si postao rendžer?

785
01:25:48,891 --> 01:25:50,643
Zasad je tocno?

786
01:25:51,931 --> 01:25:55,924
Dosje suda za maloljetnike
navodi te kao <i>amicus curiae.</i>

787
01:25:56,131 --> 01:26:01,489
Svjedocenje nepristrane osobe
presudno za sudacku odluku.

788
01:26:04,451 --> 01:26:09,571
Obicno je ono zapisano,
ali priloga u dosjeu nema.

789
01:26:14,931 --> 01:26:16,603
Tišina.

790
01:26:16,771 --> 01:26:21,720
Reci bar zašto je Haynes dobio 4 g.
zbog vožnje autom?

791
01:26:21,891 --> 01:26:26,567
Zašto nije dobio uvjetnu?
Imao je dom, oca.

792
01:26:27,371 --> 01:26:29,521
Što dosje kaže o njemu?

793
01:26:30,171 --> 01:26:35,291
Sitni lopov koji je odslužio svoje.
Izašao je i ostao cist.

794
01:26:36,131 --> 01:26:38,884
Tvoj dragocjeni dosje
tu griješi.

795
01:26:41,091 --> 01:26:42,365
U redu.

796
01:26:43,291 --> 01:26:44,929
Reci mi tada
istinu.

797
01:26:48,371 --> 01:26:53,570
Haynesov stari bio je kriminalac...

798
01:26:53,771 --> 01:26:57,559
...slab na kurve.

799
01:26:57,771 --> 01:27:03,607
No pretukao bi sve na koje je
naišao ili ih ševio.

800
01:27:03,811 --> 01:27:05,244
Da sam ja...

801
01:27:06,931 --> 01:27:09,399
Da je sudac pustio
djecaka kuci...

802
01:27:09,571 --> 01:27:13,723
...za godinu dana imao bi popis
zlocina dugacak kao tvoja ruka.

803
01:27:16,051 --> 01:27:18,485
Gatesville nije tako loš.

804
01:27:19,011 --> 01:27:23,402
Znam djecake koje je popravio.

805
01:27:25,171 --> 01:27:27,765
Jedan je cak
postao svecenik.

806
01:27:28,931 --> 01:27:30,125
Ne shvacam.

807
01:27:30,811 --> 01:27:33,086
Ne shvacaš.

808
01:27:33,571 --> 01:27:37,803
U Teksasu je važno koga poznaješ
i što ti oni duguju.

809
01:27:38,131 --> 01:27:41,726
Tako radim. Tako i ti radiš.

810
01:27:43,091 --> 01:27:45,651
Bešcutan si, zar ne?

811
01:27:46,771 --> 01:27:51,401
Pocastio sam suca odrescima
i rekao mu da osudi djecaka.

812
01:27:51,611 --> 01:27:54,648
Rekao sam mu da je tako najbolje.

813
01:27:57,211 --> 01:28:00,999
Sudac je ucinio sve
što sam predložio.

814
01:28:10,571 --> 01:28:12,721
Butch!

815
01:28:12,891 --> 01:28:14,688
Probudi se!

816
01:28:15,971 --> 01:28:17,086
Butch!

817
01:28:45,851 --> 01:28:48,160
Nisam vas htio uplašiti.

818
01:28:49,731 --> 01:28:53,690
Radim nocu. Hladnije je.

819
01:28:54,491 --> 01:28:55,810
Auto se pokvario?

820
01:28:55,971 --> 01:28:59,964
Ne. Spavamo u vašem polju.

821
01:29:00,251 --> 01:29:05,564
Polje nije moje.
Obradujem ga za g. Andrewsa.

822
01:29:05,771 --> 01:29:07,602
Odakle ste?

823
01:29:07,811 --> 01:29:10,848
Dovezli smo se jucer
iz Texarcane.

824
01:29:11,051 --> 01:29:14,043
- Dug put.
- To ste dobro rekli.

825
01:29:15,051 --> 01:29:19,522
Nema potrebe da spavate tu,
a ne na mom kaucu.

826
01:29:19,691 --> 01:29:22,683
Ne želimo smetati. Moramo ici.

827
01:29:22,851 --> 01:29:28,369
Ne smetate. Probudit cu vas
u zoru, nahraniti...

828
01:29:28,891 --> 01:29:30,290
...i možete ici.

829
01:29:36,611 --> 01:29:38,044
U redu.

830
01:30:04,571 --> 01:30:07,802
Probudio vas je? Rekla sam ti
da to ne ciniš.

831
01:30:08,011 --> 01:30:10,969
Nema štete.

832
01:30:11,891 --> 01:30:15,725
Ja sam Lottie, Mackova žena.
Ovo je moj unuk Cleveland.

833
01:30:15,931 --> 01:30:18,286
Cleve. Šest mi je godina.

834
01:30:19,371 --> 01:30:21,566
Meni je osam. Ja sam Phil...

835
01:30:23,291 --> 01:30:24,724
Buzz.

836
01:30:31,251 --> 01:30:34,049
Tu dolje imamo potok.
Hoceš ga vidjeti poslije?

837
01:30:34,211 --> 01:30:35,610
Svakako.

838
01:30:37,011 --> 01:30:38,888
- Dobro jutro.
- 'Jutro.

839
01:30:39,051 --> 01:30:41,770
- Odmorili ste se?
- Hoceš li tanjur?

840
01:30:41,931 --> 01:30:47,244
Donesi mi termosicu iz kamiona.

841
01:30:47,451 --> 01:30:49,760
Cuješ li ti mene?

842
01:30:52,891 --> 01:30:55,769
Nema pameti koliko ni kokoš.

843
01:31:11,851 --> 01:31:13,921
Hocete da ostanem
na autocesti 70?

844
01:31:14,131 --> 01:31:16,167
Ne. Kreni
prema Amarillu.

845
01:31:16,371 --> 01:31:20,569
Srest cemo se s njim ili mu mahati
kad bude prelazio granicu.

846
01:31:23,371 --> 01:31:25,885
Ucinite to ponovno!

847
01:31:28,371 --> 01:31:30,965
Gdje je djecakova majka?

848
01:31:31,451 --> 01:31:33,965
Ovaj smo je put
ostavili kod kuce.

849
01:31:34,891 --> 01:31:37,246
Muški izlazak.

850
01:31:39,171 --> 01:31:41,162
Pogledajte ovo.

851
01:31:41,331 --> 01:31:42,764
Pogledajte!

852
01:31:43,371 --> 01:31:47,967
G. Andrews nam ga je dao
kad je kupio sebi moderniji.

853
01:31:48,171 --> 01:31:49,729
Isuse!

854
01:31:56,931 --> 01:31:58,125
To je glazba!

855
01:32:07,091 --> 01:32:10,242
Ovu nisam dugo cuo.

856
01:32:10,451 --> 01:32:13,523
Stara je.

857
01:32:13,731 --> 01:32:19,681
Djevojacko prezime gde Andrews
je Bourgeois. Na pola Kreolka.

858
01:32:19,891 --> 01:32:22,485
G. Andrews nece
da se to procuje.

859
01:32:22,651 --> 01:32:25,563
Zato nam ih je dao.

860
01:32:46,771 --> 01:32:48,443
Hocete li plesati,
Lottie?

861
01:32:48,651 --> 01:32:51,961
Ja? Bože sacuvaj.

862
01:32:55,771 --> 01:32:57,682
Slijedite me.

863
01:33:13,131 --> 01:33:16,760
- G. Poe, znate plesati.
- I trebao bih znati.

864
01:33:16,931 --> 01:33:19,570
Odrastao sam u plesnoj
javnoj kuci.

865
01:33:19,731 --> 01:33:22,199
- Zafrkavate me.
- Ne.

866
01:33:24,051 --> 01:33:28,806
Moja bi mama s njima
otplesala ravno u krevet.

867
01:33:32,131 --> 01:33:33,564
Ustani, Buzz.

868
01:33:35,971 --> 01:33:39,327
Zaplešite.

869
01:33:40,131 --> 01:33:42,406
Hajde!

870
01:33:44,931 --> 01:33:46,159
Plešite, djecaci.

871
01:33:51,051 --> 01:33:52,040
Okreni me!

872
01:34:18,291 --> 01:34:21,806
<i>Terry Pugh naden je mrtav</i>
<i>u Teksasu...</i>

873
01:34:22,011 --> 01:34:26,641
<i>... prostrijeljene glave.</i>
<i>Haynes je uzeo taoca, djecaka...</i>

874
01:34:35,771 --> 01:34:38,126
Uskoro odlazimo.

875
01:34:39,131 --> 01:34:42,123
Sve cu vas ubiti ako
pokušate neku glupost.

876
01:34:47,771 --> 01:34:51,286
Što se dogodilo, Mack?
Izgledaš kao da si vidio duha.

877
01:34:51,811 --> 01:34:53,722
Idemo, Buzz.

878
01:34:53,891 --> 01:34:56,086
- Moramo krenuti.
- Okreni me.

879
01:34:56,251 --> 01:34:57,889
Dodi ovamo baki.

880
01:34:58,091 --> 01:34:59,968
- Daj!
- Ovamo!

881
01:35:00,171 --> 01:35:02,685
- Okreni me.
- Ovamo!

882
01:35:29,171 --> 01:35:31,890
Zašto si udario Clevea?

883
01:35:32,611 --> 01:35:36,001
Nije bio dovoljno brz? Zato?

884
01:35:37,851 --> 01:35:42,402
Možda se katkad uzbudi.
Možda ne cuje sve što kažeš.

885
01:35:44,651 --> 01:35:47,449
Zlo mi je od tebe.

886
01:36:01,131 --> 01:36:02,200
Uperi ga na njega.

887
01:36:02,371 --> 01:36:04,487
- Ne želim.
- Uperi ga!

888
01:36:08,451 --> 01:36:10,726
Hoceš li da te okrenem?

889
01:36:12,491 --> 01:36:14,163
Naravno da hoceš.

890
01:36:14,371 --> 01:36:19,206
Stavi ruke medu noge.
Necu te ozlijediti.

891
01:36:27,451 --> 01:36:29,760
Ne vjeruje ti više.

892
01:36:33,771 --> 01:36:35,966
Moraš zaslužiti povjerenje.

893
01:36:36,731 --> 01:36:39,484
Stavi ruke medu noge.

894
01:37:01,651 --> 01:37:04,484
Podi u auto po uže, Buzz.

895
01:37:07,651 --> 01:37:09,084
Phillipe!

896
01:37:32,531 --> 01:37:37,480
Zagrli djecaka i
reci mu da ga voliš.

897
01:37:52,531 --> 01:37:55,762
Volim te.

898
01:37:55,971 --> 01:37:59,281
Ne, starce.
Reci kao da to doista misliš.

899
01:38:00,411 --> 01:38:03,050
- Djecak zna da ga volim.
- Reci!

900
01:38:03,211 --> 01:38:04,690
Molim vas.

901
01:38:06,211 --> 01:38:08,884
Imam osjecaj.

902
01:38:09,091 --> 01:38:13,004
Znam da ste dobar covjek.

903
01:38:14,011 --> 01:38:16,479
Ne, nisam dobar covjek.

904
01:38:16,771 --> 01:38:19,126
Nisam ni najgori.

905
01:38:19,451 --> 01:38:21,567
Samo sam drukciji.

906
01:38:27,651 --> 01:38:29,323
Reci to, Mack.

907
01:38:31,171 --> 01:38:32,763
Reci!

908
01:38:34,651 --> 01:38:37,085
Ništa te ne stoji.

909
01:38:39,211 --> 01:38:40,929
Cleve...

910
01:38:43,091 --> 01:38:44,444
Volim te.

911
01:38:46,291 --> 01:38:47,883
Isuse!

912
01:38:49,291 --> 01:38:51,247
Bilo je prekrasno.

913
01:39:32,731 --> 01:39:33,959
Klekni.

914
01:39:37,731 --> 01:39:40,040
Ruke iza leda.

915
01:40:25,891 --> 01:40:28,963
Možeš cekati u autu ili gledati.

916
01:40:30,291 --> 01:40:33,089
Dovoljno si star da odluciš.

917
01:40:49,291 --> 01:40:50,929
Zažmiri, Cleve.

918
01:40:52,291 --> 01:40:54,680
Lottie,
držite cvrsto djecaka.

919
01:40:56,011 --> 01:40:57,888
I vi zažmirite.

920
01:41:02,411 --> 01:41:03,844
Molim vas...

921
01:41:04,051 --> 01:41:05,450
Kakva korist
od toga?

922
01:41:05,651 --> 01:41:09,246
Dat cu vam sve što imamo.

923
01:41:09,891 --> 01:41:14,203
Oce! Sveti se ime Tvoje.

924
01:41:14,411 --> 01:41:19,439
Dodi kraljevstvo Tvoje.
Kako na nebu tako i na zemlji.

925
01:41:19,651 --> 01:41:22,085
Mack, Cleve, molite sa mnom.

926
01:41:22,251 --> 01:41:25,129
Kruh naš svagdanji
daj nam ga danas.

927
01:41:25,331 --> 01:41:29,370
I otpusti nam grijehe naše kako
i mi otpuštamo dužnicima našim.

928
01:41:29,531 --> 01:41:33,160
I ne uvedi nas u napast
nego izbavi nas od zla.

929
01:43:19,971 --> 01:43:21,484
Phillipe?

930
01:44:47,251 --> 01:44:50,641
Hvala na gostoprimstvu.

931
01:45:13,811 --> 01:45:14,800
Phillipe!

932
01:45:27,251 --> 01:45:28,684
Što je to,
do vraga?

933
01:45:55,971 --> 01:45:59,008
Ðavolsku si stvar ucinio.

934
01:46:01,811 --> 01:46:05,360
Pravi si heroj. Sutra ce biti
u svim novinama...

935
01:46:05,571 --> 01:46:08,847
...kako si spasio te ljude.
Zapravo ih...

936
01:46:09,011 --> 01:46:12,048
...nisam namjeravao ubiti.

937
01:46:12,251 --> 01:46:16,290
Ubio sam dvojicu u životu.

938
01:46:17,091 --> 01:46:19,366
Jedan je napao
moju mamu.

939
01:46:20,331 --> 01:46:22,287
Drugi je napao tebe.

940
01:46:31,411 --> 01:46:35,529
Što kažeš da to raspravimo?

941
01:46:36,971 --> 01:46:39,326
Tada možemo
krenuti dalje.

942
01:46:43,051 --> 01:46:45,326
Dopustit cu ti
i da voziš.

943
01:46:45,531 --> 01:46:49,206
Prekrižiti to na tvom popisu.
Što kažeš?

944
01:47:28,331 --> 01:47:31,960
To je njegov auto.
Otišao je pješice.

945
01:47:32,131 --> 01:47:35,441
Ima revolver.
Mack kaže da je možda.38.

946
01:47:59,691 --> 01:48:02,000
Aljaska, Phillipe. Surova.

947
01:48:02,891 --> 01:48:06,645
Covjek protiv prirode.
Osobno, to volim.

948
01:48:07,091 --> 01:48:09,559
Jesam li ti rekao da
ondje živi moj tata?

949
01:48:12,051 --> 01:48:13,564
On je...

950
01:48:15,251 --> 01:48:18,163
On mi je i poslao razglednicu.

951
01:48:18,931 --> 01:48:22,003
Slušaj što piše. " Dragi Roberte.

952
01:48:22,331 --> 01:48:28,008
Znaj da moj odlazak
nema veze s tobom.

953
01:48:28,611 --> 01:48:33,446
Aljaska je predivna i uglavnom
hladnija od pakla.

954
01:48:33,651 --> 01:48:37,405
Jednog ceš me dana posjetiti...

955
01:48:37,611 --> 01:48:41,320
...i možda se tada bolje upoznamo."

956
01:48:44,291 --> 01:48:45,963
Kratko i jasno.

957
01:48:46,531 --> 01:48:48,761
To je stil moga staroga.

958
01:48:52,011 --> 01:48:55,970
Odmorit cemo se malo.

959
01:48:58,051 --> 01:49:00,690
Tada ti odluci.

960
01:49:02,931 --> 01:49:04,683
Što kažeš, Phillipe?

961
01:49:08,851 --> 01:49:11,411
Viden je u Happyju
u okrugu Swisher.

962
01:49:11,571 --> 01:49:15,166
Javi radio vezom.
Neka ne prenagljuju.

963
01:49:15,331 --> 01:49:19,290
Guverner šalje majku.
Da bude spremna?

964
01:49:19,451 --> 01:49:22,284
- Dobra ideja.
- Neka je dovezu helikopterom.

965
01:49:34,531 --> 01:49:37,250
Jedno je sigurno.

966
01:49:38,411 --> 01:49:41,403
Odsad vjerujem u duhove.

967
01:49:44,571 --> 01:49:46,960
Nikad me još nisu ranili.

968
01:49:47,171 --> 01:49:48,445
Žao mi je.

969
01:49:49,131 --> 01:49:51,281
Znam da jest.

970
01:50:02,771 --> 01:50:07,401
Ali ako se to moralo dogoditi...

971
01:50:07,611 --> 01:50:09,920
...drago mi je što si
to ucinio ti...

972
01:50:12,691 --> 01:50:15,524
...a ne netko koga
i ne poznajem.

973
01:50:16,571 --> 01:50:18,846
Kad sve odvagnemo...

974
01:50:20,291 --> 01:50:22,521
...osjecam se
sasvim dobro.

975
01:50:37,131 --> 01:50:38,280
Momci,
slušajte.

976
01:50:39,811 --> 01:50:41,005
Bježi!

977
01:50:44,251 --> 01:50:45,684
Necu, Phillipe.

978
01:50:47,971 --> 01:50:51,327
Za onamo kamo idem
trebam vremeplov...

979
01:50:51,811 --> 01:50:54,200
...s kreštavim radijom.

980
01:50:57,091 --> 01:50:59,400
Hodanje je za staromodne.

981
01:51:11,491 --> 01:51:15,006
- Misliš da ce ubiti djecaka?
- Nece.

982
01:51:17,971 --> 01:51:20,166
Tom Hendricks, F.B.I.

983
01:51:20,331 --> 01:51:23,209
- Jedan od naših je s vama.
- Jest.

984
01:51:23,411 --> 01:51:25,481
- Opkolili smo podrucje.
- Dobro?

985
01:51:25,691 --> 01:51:29,286
Stisnuto je sve poput šupka.
Pardon.

986
01:51:29,491 --> 01:51:32,927
Zacijelo usporedba
iz osobnog iskustva.

987
01:51:37,811 --> 01:51:38,800
Gdje su?

988
01:51:38,971 --> 01:51:41,246
Pokraj drveta uz jezerce.

989
01:51:41,411 --> 01:51:44,687
Murjaci su ih opkolili.

990
01:51:45,651 --> 01:51:47,926
Dopuštate
da ja to riješim?

991
01:51:51,731 --> 01:51:54,199
Možemo to zajedno riješiti.

992
01:51:57,091 --> 01:51:58,080
Bradley!

993
01:51:58,291 --> 01:52:00,202
Daj mi megafon.

994
01:52:00,411 --> 01:52:02,527
Još nešto.

995
01:52:02,731 --> 01:52:05,689
Haynes je ranjen. Djecak
je pucao na njega.

996
01:52:06,691 --> 01:52:08,170
Šalite se?

997
01:52:10,971 --> 01:52:13,405
Megafon.

998
01:52:19,691 --> 01:52:23,286
Butch Haynes! Ja sam rendžer
Red Garnett.

999
01:52:23,451 --> 01:52:27,160
Znam da si ranjen. Imamo
20-30 naoružanih ljudi.

1000
01:52:27,331 --> 01:52:29,447
Pogledaj, vidjet ceš
da je istina.

1001
01:52:29,811 --> 01:52:35,169
Sve to zbog mene? Dirljivo.
Ipak, morat cete se povuci.

1002
01:52:35,651 --> 01:52:37,164
Idem u Meksiko.

1003
01:52:37,411 --> 01:52:39,606
Tada ideš u
pogrešnom smjeru.

1004
01:52:40,171 --> 01:52:41,729
Varam ih, dakako.

1005
01:52:41,891 --> 01:52:46,123
Pusti djecaka i razgovarat cemo.

1006
01:52:46,531 --> 01:52:49,762
Hvala na ponudi, kapetane.

1007
01:52:51,131 --> 01:52:54,487
Ali znate da to ne mogu.

1008
01:52:55,451 --> 01:52:59,603
Povucite se i...

1009
01:52:59,811 --> 01:53:02,689
...ostavit cu djecaka
na granici.

1010
01:53:03,451 --> 01:53:07,808
Ne pristanete li,
pucat cu mu u glavu.

1011
01:53:08,571 --> 01:53:10,004
Mislim ozbiljno!

1012
01:53:14,851 --> 01:53:17,206
Ne gledaj me tako.

1013
01:53:18,131 --> 01:53:20,440
Nemam ni revolvera.

1014
01:53:25,971 --> 01:53:28,849
Usput, gdje je nestao?

1015
01:53:30,731 --> 01:53:32,926
Bacio sam ga u bunar.

1016
01:53:37,291 --> 01:53:38,724
Pametno!

1017
01:53:39,371 --> 01:53:41,839
Ako pobjegnu,
opet smo na pocetku.

1018
01:53:42,011 --> 01:53:46,368
- Osudit ce ga na elektricnu stolicu.
- Ubio je dvoje ljudi u dva dana.

1019
01:53:46,531 --> 01:53:50,649
- Ne znamo je li ih on ubio.
- Nije sjedio kod kuce.

1020
01:53:50,811 --> 01:53:54,804
- Tko bi ubio Pugha? Možda Casper?
- Dosta!

1021
01:53:55,091 --> 01:53:58,800
Kako sada stvari stoje,
to i nije važno.

1022
01:53:59,931 --> 01:54:03,765
- Trebamo izvuci djecaka.
- Gdje želite da budem?

1023
01:54:03,971 --> 01:54:07,407
Uz auto.
Znaš li baratati time?

1024
01:54:07,611 --> 01:54:10,842
Znam. Oprostite.

1025
01:54:30,531 --> 01:54:32,044
Vidiš, Phillipe?

1026
01:54:33,971 --> 01:54:36,166
Snovi se ostvaruju.

1027
01:54:37,371 --> 01:54:42,161
- Evo tvoje rakete.
- Misliš da cu se voziti u tome?

1028
01:54:43,131 --> 01:54:44,928
Baš danas.

1029
01:54:45,251 --> 01:54:48,846
- Djecakova majka.
- Pomozi joj da izade.

1030
01:55:06,531 --> 01:55:09,603
Hej, Butch!
Imamo djecakovu majku!

1031
01:55:17,091 --> 01:55:20,766
- Što je?
- To je moja mama.

1032
01:55:21,731 --> 01:55:25,929
Imaš vec kostim duha.

1033
01:55:26,171 --> 01:55:28,731
Hoce li ti dopustiti
da ideš u maškare?

1034
01:55:29,651 --> 01:55:31,642
Vec sam bio
u jednoj kuci.

1035
01:55:33,371 --> 01:55:34,520
Dodi.

1036
01:55:39,571 --> 01:55:43,530
Stavi... Stavi opet masku.

1037
01:55:46,531 --> 01:55:48,920
Okreni se i uplaši ih.

1038
01:55:49,651 --> 01:55:54,042
Molim vas! On mi je jedini sin!

1039
01:55:54,451 --> 01:55:57,170
Dat cu vam novac!
Sve što imam!

1040
01:55:57,371 --> 01:56:01,159
Molim vas!
Samo da ga povedem kuci!

1041
01:56:02,371 --> 01:56:04,123
Proklet bio.

1042
01:56:04,331 --> 01:56:06,765
Dajte da vidim.

1043
01:56:06,931 --> 01:56:09,286
Jesi li spreman
da ideš doma?

1044
01:56:11,651 --> 01:56:13,084
Jesam.

1045
01:56:15,291 --> 01:56:19,489
Kapetane! Imate li slatkiša?

1046
01:56:20,291 --> 01:56:21,280
Što?

1047
01:56:21,491 --> 01:56:25,882
Slatkiša! Za maškare!
Kuglica od kokica!

1048
01:56:26,091 --> 01:56:28,924
Ušecerenih jabuka!
Takve gluposti!

1049
01:56:29,091 --> 01:56:30,206
Gladni ste?!

1050
01:56:30,411 --> 01:56:33,403
Nabavite slatkiše...

1051
01:56:34,411 --> 01:56:36,288
...i vratit cu vam duha.

1052
01:56:37,571 --> 01:56:39,004
Skupite slatkiše.

1053
01:56:39,171 --> 01:56:41,731
Imate li žvakacih guma?

1054
01:56:41,891 --> 01:56:43,961
Slatkiša? Juicy Fruit?

1055
01:56:44,131 --> 01:56:46,850
Idemo! Hajde.
Nemamo vremena.

1056
01:56:47,011 --> 01:56:50,367
Mama mora obecati da ce ga
svake godine voditi u maškare!

1057
01:56:50,891 --> 01:56:54,850
- Spreman?
- Recite samo kada.

1058
01:56:55,051 --> 01:56:56,928
Daj mi popis.

1059
01:56:57,091 --> 01:56:59,161
Popis!

1060
01:57:02,691 --> 01:57:03,885
Još nešto!

1061
01:57:04,251 --> 01:57:07,960
Mora obecati
da ce ga voditi na tobogan!

1062
01:57:08,171 --> 01:57:13,291
Kupiti mu šecernu vunu kad god poželi!

1063
01:57:16,851 --> 01:57:20,810
Želim ici doma. Moja mama
nije loša. Daje mi sve to.

1064
01:57:22,251 --> 01:57:24,207
Ne laži.

1065
01:57:30,051 --> 01:57:34,522
Znam kako se osjecaš.

1066
01:57:35,011 --> 01:57:36,603
Obecava!

1067
01:57:38,211 --> 01:57:40,122
Neka to kaže!

1068
01:57:43,651 --> 01:57:45,243
Obecavam.

1069
01:57:45,451 --> 01:57:50,525
- Možemo li joj vjerovati?
- Dobra je mama.

1070
01:57:54,691 --> 01:57:58,445
Kada dodeš doma, sakrij to.

1071
01:58:01,251 --> 01:58:04,641
Ti nisi loš, zar ne?

1072
01:58:07,731 --> 01:58:09,164
Aha.

1073
01:58:11,011 --> 01:58:12,649
Slušaj, Buzz.

1074
01:58:12,851 --> 01:58:14,364
Želim da...

1075
01:58:15,171 --> 01:58:19,130
Kreni vrlo polako...

1076
01:58:19,331 --> 01:58:21,606
...s rukama u zraku.

1077
01:58:21,811 --> 01:58:25,440
Kreni ravno prema policajcima...

1078
01:58:26,691 --> 01:58:29,080
...i vici: "Maškare!"

1079
01:58:30,851 --> 01:58:35,561
- Što ceš ti raditi?
- Nešto cu smisliti.

1080
01:58:44,131 --> 01:58:45,564
Bok, Phillipe.

1081
01:58:46,851 --> 01:58:48,762
Bilo je vraško
putovanje.

1082
01:58:53,251 --> 01:58:55,811
Kapetane!

1083
01:58:55,971 --> 01:59:00,806
Pripremite se za Caspera,
ljubaznog duha!

1084
01:59:02,171 --> 01:59:04,127
Najljubazniji duh
kojega poznajem.

1085
01:59:08,731 --> 01:59:10,881
Navuci masku.

1086
01:59:12,331 --> 01:59:14,686
Ruke u vis.

1087
01:59:18,291 --> 01:59:22,000
Idi i reci im kako sam ti rekao.

1088
01:59:22,411 --> 01:59:23,844
Rede.

1089
01:59:24,451 --> 01:59:26,442
Pogledaj!

1090
01:59:27,371 --> 01:59:29,009
Što to radi?

1091
01:59:30,331 --> 01:59:32,162
Djecace,
nastavi hodati.

1092
01:59:48,331 --> 01:59:49,559
Hodaj, djecace!

1093
01:59:54,051 --> 01:59:57,600
- Pozovite sina.
- Trci!

1094
01:59:57,811 --> 02:00:01,884
Phillipe, dušo, požuri se!

1095
02:00:02,051 --> 02:00:05,726
- Ponovno je uzeo taoca.
- Kamo ide?

1096
02:00:17,931 --> 02:00:23,051
Mislim da smo izborili dobre uvjete.

1097
02:00:23,491 --> 02:00:26,324
Želiš li još što?

1098
02:00:27,851 --> 02:00:30,285
Žele li te ubiti?

1099
02:00:55,091 --> 02:00:57,082
Budi spreman.

1100
02:01:10,731 --> 02:01:12,642
Sad sam sve vidio.

1101
02:01:13,131 --> 02:01:16,441
- Što je naumio?
- Proklet bio ako znam.

1102
02:01:16,851 --> 02:01:18,842
Predat ce se.

1103
02:01:19,011 --> 02:01:21,081
Držite na umu da je
još naoružan.

1104
02:01:23,051 --> 02:01:28,250
Vjerojatno možemo zaboraviti Aljasku.

1105
02:01:30,371 --> 02:01:34,046
Imamo naoružanog ubojicu
i nevina djecaka.

1106
02:01:35,051 --> 02:01:38,282
- Meta je jasna?
- Jest.

1107
02:01:38,491 --> 02:01:40,925
Drži ga na nišanu.

1108
02:01:41,331 --> 02:01:43,322
Ne pucaj
dok ne kažem.

1109
02:01:43,731 --> 02:01:45,926
Kamo idete?

1110
02:02:14,411 --> 02:02:15,844
Nenaoružan sam.

1111
02:02:17,211 --> 02:02:19,008
Baci oružje.

1112
02:02:19,251 --> 02:02:21,845
Da imam revolver...

1113
02:02:23,571 --> 02:02:26,529
...vec bih išao u
suprotnom smjeru.

1114
02:02:27,291 --> 02:02:31,603
Moj se partner riješio dokaza.

1115
02:02:36,411 --> 02:02:38,083
Poznajem li ja vas,
prijatelju?

1116
02:02:40,091 --> 02:02:42,764
Ne.

1117
02:02:45,891 --> 02:02:50,123
Želim razgovarati s djecakom.

1118
02:02:50,331 --> 02:02:53,641
Tada možemo obaviti posao.

1119
02:02:53,851 --> 02:02:54,840
Što kažete?

1120
02:02:55,331 --> 02:02:57,640
Bit cu kratak.

1121
02:02:59,771 --> 02:03:00,760
Može.

1122
02:03:08,051 --> 02:03:09,882
Želim ti nešto dati.

1123
02:03:10,051 --> 02:03:12,167
Drži ga na nišanu.
Ako se samo pomakne...

1124
02:03:12,571 --> 02:03:14,562
Cekaj!

1125
02:03:19,611 --> 02:03:22,205
Možda ceš jednom poci.

1126
02:03:22,371 --> 02:03:24,123
Poseže za oružjem!

1127
02:03:26,851 --> 02:03:28,000
Ne!

1128
02:03:33,731 --> 02:03:35,164
Butch!

1129
02:03:38,211 --> 02:03:43,205
Kvragu! Prostrijeljen
dvaput u jednome danu.

1130
02:03:58,251 --> 02:04:03,006
Ne brinite se.
Sad ne može nikome nauditi.

1131
02:04:03,411 --> 02:04:05,402
Gospode Bože!

1132
02:04:08,771 --> 02:04:11,160
Nije naoružan.

1133
02:05:51,611 --> 02:05:53,044
- Odbij!
- Mirno!

1134
02:05:53,251 --> 02:05:57,324
- Što je to bilo?
- Nisam rekao "kada".

1135
02:06:06,891 --> 02:06:08,324
Kvragu!

1136
02:06:09,291 --> 02:06:12,249
I ja sam mislio da je naoružan.

1137
02:06:12,451 --> 02:06:15,090
Nismo mogli znati.

1138
02:06:35,171 --> 02:06:38,561
Ucinio si sve što si mogao.

1139
02:06:38,771 --> 02:06:40,443
Znaš to.

1140
02:06:43,491 --> 02:06:45,880
Ništa ne znam.

1141
02:06:48,651 --> 02:06:51,324
Baš ništa.

